description:
Pokemon GO Bulbasaur is a grass poison type with 981 MAX CP.
Bulbasaur best moveset is Vine Whip and Power Whip.
Bulbasaur is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Psychic type moves.
Bulbasaur is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Bulbasaur
pokedexEntry: Bulbasaur can be seen napping in bright sunlight. There is a seed on its back. By soaking up the sun's rays, the seed grows progressively larger.

description:
Pokemon GO Ivysaur is a grass poison type with 1552 MAX CP.
Ivysaur best moveset is Vine Whip and Solar Beam.
Ivysaur is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Psychic type moves.
Ivysaur is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Ivysaur
pokedexEntry: There is a bud on this Pokemon's back. To support its weight, Ivysaur's legs and trunk grow thick and strong. If it starts spending more time lying in the sunlight, it's a sign that the bud will bloom into a large flower soon.

description:
Pokemon GO Venusaur is a grass poison type with 2568 MAX CP.
Venusaur best moveset is Vine Whip and Solar Beam.
Venusaur is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Psychic type moves.
Venusaur is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
name: Venusaur
pokedexEntry: There is a large flower on Venusaur's back. The flower is said to take on vivid colors if it gets plenty of nutrition and sunlight. The flower's aroma soothes the emotions of people.

description:
Pokemon GO Charmander is a fire type with 831 MAX CP.
Charmander best moveset is Ember and Flamethrower.
Charmander is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Charmander is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Charmander
pokedexEntry: The flame that burns at the tip of its tail is an indication of its emotions. The flame wavers when Charmander is enjoying itself. If the Pokemon becomes enraged, the flame burns fiercely.

description:
Pokemon GO Charmeleon is a fire type with 1484 MAX CP.
Charmeleon best moveset is Fire Fang and Flamethrower.
Charmeleon is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Charmeleon is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Charmeleon
pokedexEntry: Charmeleon mercilessly destroys its foes using its sharp claws. If it encounters a strong foe, it turns aggressive. In this excited state, the flame at the tip of its tail flares with a bluish white color.

description:
Pokemon GO Charizard is a fire flying type with 2686 MAX CP.
Charizard best moveset is Fire Spin and Overheat.
Charizard is vulnerable to Rock, Water, Electric type moves.
Charizard is boosted by Clear and Wind weather.
name: Charizard
pokedexEntry: Charizard flies around the sky in search of powerful opponents. It breathes fire of such great heat that it melts anything. However, it never turns its fiery breath on any opponent weaker than itself.

description:
Pokemon GO Squirtle is a water type with 808 MAX CP.
Squirtle best moveset is Bubble and Aqua Tail.
Squirtle is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Squirtle is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Squirtle
pokedexEntry: Squirtle's shell is not merely used for protection. The shell's rounded shape and the grooves on its surface help minimize resistance in water, enabling this Pokemon to swim at high speeds.

description:
Pokemon GO Wartortle is a water type with 1324 MAX CP.
Wartortle best moveset is Bite and Hydro Pump.
Wartortle is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Wartortle is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Wartortle
pokedexEntry: Its tail is large and covered with a rich, thick fur. The tail becomes increasingly deeper in color as Wartortle ages. The scratches on its shell are evidence of this Pokemon's toughness as a battler.

description:
Pokemon GO Blastoise is a water type with 2291 MAX CP.
Blastoise best moveset is Bite and Hydro Pump.
Blastoise is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Blastoise is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Blastoise
pokedexEntry: Blastoise has water spouts that protrude from its shell. The water spouts are very accurate. They can shoot bullets of water with enough accuracy to strike empty cans from a distance of over 160 feet.

description:
Pokemon GO Caterpie is a bug type with 393 MAX CP.
Caterpie best moveset is Tackle and Struggle.
Caterpie is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock type moves.
Caterpie is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 12 candy to evolve!
name: Caterpie
pokedexEntry: Caterpie has a voracious appetite. It can devour leaves bigger than its body right before your eyes. From its antenna, this Pokemon releases a terrifically strong odor.

description:
Pokemon GO Metapod is a bug type with 419 MAX CP.
Metapod best moveset is Tackle and Struggle.
Metapod is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock type moves.
Metapod is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Metapod
pokedexEntry: The shell covering this Pokemon's body is as hard as an iron slab. Metapod does not move very much. It stays still because it is preparing its soft innards for evolution inside the hard shell.

description:
Pokemon GO Butterfree is a bug flying type with 1701 MAX CP.
Butterfree best moveset is Bug Bite and Bug Buzz.
Butterfree is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Butterfree is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Butterfree
pokedexEntry: Butterfree has a superior ability to search for delicious honey from flowers. It can even search out, extract, and carry honey from flowers that are blooming over six miles from its nest.

description:
Pokemon GO Weedle is a bug poison type with 397 MAX CP.
Weedle best moveset is Bug Bite and Struggle.
Weedle is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Psychic type moves.
Weedle is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
It takes 12 candy to evolve!
name: Weedle
pokedexEntry: Weedle has an extremely acute sense of smell. It is capable of distinguishing its favorite kinds of leaves from those it dislikes just by sniffing with its big red proboscis (nose).

description:
Pokemon GO Kakuna is a bug poison type with 392 MAX CP.
Kakuna best moveset is Bug Bite and Struggle.
Kakuna is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Psychic type moves.
Kakuna is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Kakuna
pokedexEntry: Kakuna remains virtually immobile as it clings to a tree. However, on the inside, it is extremely busy as it prepares for its coming evolution. This is evident from how hot the shell becomes to the touch.

description:
Pokemon GO Beedrill is a bug poison type with 1777 MAX CP.
Beedrill best moveset is Bug Bite and Sludge Bomb.
Beedrill is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Psychic type moves.
Beedrill is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
name: Beedrill
pokedexEntry: Beedrill is extremely territorial. No one should ever approach its nest—this is for their own safety. If angered, they will attack in a furious swarm.

description:
Pokemon GO Pidgey is a normal flying type with 580 MAX CP.
Pidgey best moveset is Quick Attack and Aerial Ace.
Pidgey is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Pidgey is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
It takes 12 candy to evolve!
name: Pidgey
pokedexEntry: Pidgey has an extremely sharp sense of direction. It is capable of unerringly returning home to its nest, however far it may be removed from its familiar surroundings.

description:
Pokemon GO Pidgeotto is a normal flying type with 1085 MAX CP.
Pidgeotto best moveset is Steel Wing and Aerial Ace.
Pidgeotto is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Pidgeotto is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Pidgeotto
pokedexEntry: Pidgeotto claims a large area as its own territory. This Pokemon flies around, patrolling its living space. If its territory is violated, it shows no mercy in thoroughly punishing the foe with its sharp claws.

description:
Pokemon GO Pidgeot is a normal flying type with 1994 MAX CP.
Pidgeot best moveset is Wing Attack and Hurricane.
Pidgeot is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Pidgeot is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
name: Pidgeot
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon has a dazzling plumage of beautifully glossy feathers. Many Trainers are captivated by the striking beauty of the feathers on its head, compelling them to choose Pidgeot as their Pokemon.

description:
Pokemon GO Rattata is a normal type with 588 MAX CP.
Rattata best moveset is Quick Attack and Hyper Fang.
Rattata is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Rattata is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Rattata
pokedexEntry: Rattata is cautious in the extreme. Even while it is asleep, it constantly listens by moving its ears around. It is not picky about where it lives—it will make its nest anywhere.

description:
Pokemon GO Raticate is a normal type with 1549 MAX CP.
Raticate best moveset is Quick Attack and Hyper Beam.
Raticate is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Raticate is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Raticate
pokedexEntry: Raticate's sturdy fangs grow steadily. To keep them ground down, it gnaws on rocks and logs. It may even chew on the walls of houses.

description:
Pokemon GO Spearow is a normal flying type with 673 MAX CP.
Spearow best moveset is Quick Attack and Sky Attack.
Spearow is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Spearow is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Spearow
pokedexEntry: Spearow has a very loud cry that can be heard over half a mile away. If its high, keening cry is heard echoing all around, it is a sign that they are warning each other of danger.

description:
Pokemon GO Fearow is a normal flying type with 1814 MAX CP.
Fearow best moveset is Steel Wing and Sky Attack.
Fearow is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Fearow is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
name: Fearow
pokedexEntry: Fearow is recognized by its long neck and elongated beak. They are conveniently shaped for catching prey in soil or water. It deftly moves its long and skinny beak to pluck prey.

description:
Pokemon GO Ekans is a poison type with 778 MAX CP.
Ekans best moveset is Acid and Sludge Bomb.
Ekans is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Ekans is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Ekans
pokedexEntry: Ekans curls itself up in a spiral while it rests. Assuming this position allows it to quickly respond to a threat from any direction with a glare from its upraised head.

description:
Pokemon GO Arbok is a poison type with 1737 MAX CP.
Arbok best moveset is Bite and Gunk Shot.
Arbok is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Arbok is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Arbok
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon is terrifically strong in order to constrict things with its body. It can even flatten steel oil drums. Once Arbok wraps its body around its foe, escaping its crunching embrace is impossible.

description:
Pokemon GO Pikachu is a electric type with 787 MAX CP.
Pikachu best moveset is Thunder Shock and Wild Charge.
Pikachu is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Pikachu is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Pikachu
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon has electricity-storing pouches on its cheeks. These appear to become electrically charged during the night while Pikachu sleeps. It occasionally discharges electricity when it is dozy after waking up.

description:
Pokemon GO Raichu is a electric type with 2025 MAX CP.
Raichu best moveset is Thunder Shock and Wild Charge.
Raichu is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Raichu is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Raichu
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon exudes a weak electrical charge from all over its body that makes it take on a slight glow in darkness. Raichu plants its tail in the ground to discharge electricity.

description:
Pokemon GO Sandshrew is a ground type with 1194 MAX CP.
Sandshrew best moveset is Mud Shot and Dig.
Sandshrew is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water type moves.
Sandshrew is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Sandshrew
pokedexEntry: Sandshrew has a very dry hide that is extremely tough. The Pokemon can roll into a ball that repels any attack. At night, it burrows into the desert sand to sleep.

description:
Pokemon GO Sandslash is a ground type with 2328 MAX CP.
Sandslash best moveset is Mud Shot and Earthquake.
Sandslash is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water type moves.
Sandslash is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Sandslash
pokedexEntry: Sandslash can roll up its body as if it were a ball covered with large spikes. In battle, this Pokemon will try to make the foe flinch by jabbing it with its spines. It then leaps at the stunned foe to tear wildly with its sharp claws.

description:
Pokemon GO Nidoran♀ is a poison type with 736 MAX CP.
Nidoran♀ best moveset is Poison Sting and Sludge Bomb.
Nidoran♀ is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Nidoran♀ is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Nidoran♀
pokedexEntry: Nidoran♀ has barbs that secrete a powerful poison. They are thought to have developed as protection for this small-bodied Pokemon. When enraged, it releases a horrible toxin from its horn.

description:
Pokemon GO Nidorina is a poison type with 1218 MAX CP.
Nidorina best moveset is Poison Sting and Sludge Bomb.
Nidorina is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Nidorina is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Nidorina
pokedexEntry: When Nidorina are with their friends or family, they keep their barbs tucked away to prevent hurting each other. This Pokemon appears to become nervous if separated from the others.

description:
Pokemon GO Nidoqueen is a poison ground type with 2338 MAX CP.
Nidoqueen best moveset is Poison Jab and Earthquake.
Nidoqueen is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic, Ice, Water type moves.
Nidoqueen is boosted by Cloudy and Clear weather.
name: Nidoqueen
pokedexEntry: Nidoqueen's body is encased in extremely hard scales. It is adept at sending foes flying with harsh tackles. This Pokemon is at its strongest when it is defending its young.

description:
Pokemon GO Nidoran♂ is a poison type with 739 MAX CP.
Nidoran♂ best moveset is Poison Sting and Sludge Bomb.
Nidoran♂ is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Nidoran♂ is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Nidoran♂
pokedexEntry: Nidoran♂ has developed muscles for moving its ears. Thanks to them, the ears can be freely moved in any direction. Even the slightest sound does not escape this Pokemon's notice.

description:
Pokemon GO Nidorino is a poison type with 1252 MAX CP.
Nidorino best moveset is Poison Jab and Sludge Bomb.
Nidorino is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Nidorino is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Nidorino
pokedexEntry: Nidorino has a horn that is harder than a diamond. If it senses a hostile presence, all the barbs on its back bristle up at once, and it challenges the foe with all its might.

description:
Pokemon GO Nidoking is a poison ground type with 2386 MAX CP.
Nidoking best moveset is Poison Jab and Earthquake.
Nidoking is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic, Ice, Water type moves.
Nidoking is boosted by Cloudy and Clear weather.
name: Nidoking
pokedexEntry: Nidoking's thick tail packs enormously destructive power. With one swing, it can topple a metal transmission tower. Once this Pokemon goes on a rampage, there is no stopping it.

description:
Pokemon GO Clefairy is a fairy type with 1085 MAX CP.
Clefairy best moveset is Pound and Moonblast.
Clefairy is vulnerable to Poison, Steel type moves.
Clefairy is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Clefairy
pokedexEntry: On every night of a full moon, groups of this Pokemon come out to play. When dawn arrives, the tired Clefairy return to their quiet mountain retreats and go to sleep nestled up against each other.

description:
Pokemon GO Clefable is a fairy type with 2353 MAX CP.
Clefable best moveset is Pound and Dazzling Gleam.
Clefable is vulnerable to Poison, Steel type moves.
Clefable is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Clefable
pokedexEntry: Clefable moves by skipping lightly as if it were flying using its wings. Its bouncy step lets it even walk on water. It is known to take strolls on lakes on quiet, moonlit nights.

description:
Pokemon GO Vulpix is a fire type with 774 MAX CP.
Vulpix best moveset is Ember and Flamethrower.
Vulpix is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Vulpix is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Vulpix
pokedexEntry: Inside Vulpix's body burns a flame that never goes out. During the daytime, when the temperatures rise, this Pokemon releases flames from its mouth to prevent its body from growing too hot.

description:
Pokemon GO Ninetales is a fire type with 2157 MAX CP.
Ninetales best moveset is Fire Spin and Overheat.
Ninetales is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Ninetales is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Ninetales
pokedexEntry: Legend has it that Ninetales came into being when nine wizards possessing sacred powers merged into one. This Pokemon is highly intelligent—it can understand human speech.

description:
Pokemon GO Jigglypuff is a normal fairy type with 713 MAX CP.
Jigglypuff best moveset is Pound and Dazzling Gleam.
Jigglypuff is vulnerable to Poison, Steel type moves.
Jigglypuff is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Jigglypuff
pokedexEntry: When this Pokemon sings, it never pauses to breathe. If it is in a battle against an opponent that does not easily fall asleep, Jigglypuff cannot breathe, endangering its life.

description:
Pokemon GO Wigglytuff is a normal fairy type with 1906 MAX CP.
Wigglytuff best moveset is Pound and Hyper Beam.
Wigglytuff is vulnerable to Poison, Steel type moves.
Wigglytuff is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Cloudy weather.
name: Wigglytuff
pokedexEntry: Wigglytuff's body is very flexible. By inhaling deeply, this Pokemon can inflate itself seemingly without end. Once inflated, Wigglytuff bounces along lightly like a balloon.

description:
Pokemon GO Zubat is a poison flying type with 569 MAX CP.
Zubat best moveset is Quick Attack and Sludge Bomb.
Zubat is vulnerable to Psychic, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Zubat is boosted by Cloudy and Wind weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Zubat
pokedexEntry: Zubat avoids sunlight because exposure causes it to become unhealthy. During the daytime, it stays in caves or under the eaves of old houses, sleeping while hanging upside down.

description:
Pokemon GO Golbat is a poison flying type with 1830 MAX CP.
Golbat best moveset is Wing Attack and Shadow Ball.
Golbat is vulnerable to Psychic, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Golbat is boosted by Cloudy and Wind weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Golbat
pokedexEntry: Golbat bites down on prey with its four fangs and drinks the victim's blood. It becomes active on inky dark moonless nights, flying around to attack people and Pokemon.

description:
Pokemon GO Oddish is a grass poison type with 1069 MAX CP.
Oddish best moveset is Acid and Sludge Bomb.
Oddish is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Psychic type moves.
Oddish is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Oddish
pokedexEntry: Oddish searches for fertile, nutrient-rich soil, then plants itself. During the daytime, while it is planted, this Pokemon's feet are thought to change shape and become similar to the roots of trees.

description:
Pokemon GO Gloom is a grass poison type with 1512 MAX CP.
Gloom best moveset is Acid and Sludge Bomb.
Gloom is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Psychic type moves.
Gloom is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Gloom
pokedexEntry: From its mouth Gloom drips honey that smells absolutely horrible. Apparently, it loves the horrid stench. It sniffs the noxious fumes and then drools even more of its honey.

description:
Pokemon GO Vileplume is a grass poison type with 2367 MAX CP.
Vileplume best moveset is Acid and Solar Beam.
Vileplume is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Psychic type moves.
Vileplume is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
name: Vileplume
pokedexEntry: Vileplume has the world's largest petals. They are used to attract prey that are then doused with toxic spores. Once the prey are immobilized, this Pokemon catches and devours them.

description:
Pokemon GO Paras is a bug grass type with 836 MAX CP.
Paras best moveset is Bug Bite and X Scissor.
Paras is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Bug, Poison, Ice type moves.
Paras is boosted by Rain and Clear
name: Paras
pokedexEntry: Paras has parasitic mushrooms growing on its back called tochukaso. They grow large by drawing nutrients from this Bug Pokemon host. They are highly valued as a medicine for extending life.

description:
Pokemon GO Parasect is a bug grass type with 1657 MAX CP.
Parasect best moveset is Fury Cutter and Solar Beam.
Parasect is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Bug, Poison, Ice type moves.
Parasect is boosted by Rain and Clear
name: Parasect
pokedexEntry: Parasect is known to infest large trees en masse and drain nutrients from the lower trunk and roots. When an infested tree dies, they move onto another tree all at once.

description:
Pokemon GO Venonat is a bug poison type with 902 MAX CP.
Venonat best moveset is Bug Bite and Signal Beam.
Venonat is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Psychic type moves.
Venonat is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Venonat
pokedexEntry: Venonat is said to have evolved with a coat of thin, stiff hair that covers its entire body for protection. It possesses large eyes that never fail to spot even minuscule prey.

description:
Pokemon GO Venomoth is a bug poison type with 1937 MAX CP.
Venomoth best moveset is Bug Bite and Bug Buzz.
Venomoth is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Psychic type moves.
Venomoth is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
name: Venomoth
pokedexEntry: Venomoth is nocturnal—it is a Pokemon that only becomes active at night. Its favorite prey are small insects that gather around streetlights, attracted by the light in the darkness.

description:
Pokemon GO Diglett is a ground type with 465 MAX CP.
Diglett best moveset is Mud Shot and Mud Bomb.
Diglett is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water type moves.
Diglett is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Diglett
pokedexEntry: Diglett are raised in most farms. The reason is simple— wherever this Pokemon burrows, the soil is left perfectly tilled for planting crops. This soil is made ideal for growing delicious vegetables.

description:
Pokemon GO Dugtrio is a ground type with 1333 MAX CP.
Dugtrio best moveset is Mud Shot and Earthquake.
Dugtrio is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water type moves.
Dugtrio is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Dugtrio
pokedexEntry: Dugtrio are actually triplets that emerged from one body. As a result, each triplet thinks exactly like the other two triplets. They work cooperatively to burrow endlessly.

description:
Pokemon GO Meowth is a normal type with 638 MAX CP.
Meowth best moveset is Scratch and Body Slam.
Meowth is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Meowth is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Meowth
pokedexEntry: Meowth withdraws its sharp claws into its paws to slinkily sneak about without making any incriminating footsteps. For some reason, this Pokemon loves shiny coins that glitter with light.

description:
Pokemon GO Persian is a normal type with 1539 MAX CP.
Persian best moveset is Scratch and Play Rough.
Persian is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Persian is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Persian
pokedexEntry: Persian has six bold whiskers that give it a look of toughness. The whiskers sense air movements to determine what is in the Pokemon's surrounding vicinity. It becomes docile if grabbed by the whiskers.

description:
Pokemon GO Psyduck is a water type with 966 MAX CP.
Psyduck best moveset is Water Gun and Aqua Tail.
Psyduck is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Psyduck is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Psyduck
pokedexEntry: If it uses its mysterious power, Psyduck can't remember having done so. It apparently can't form a memory of such an event because it goes into an altered state that is much like deep sleep.

description:
Pokemon GO Golduck is a water type with 2270 MAX CP.
Golduck best moveset is Water Gun and Hydro Pump.
Golduck is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Golduck is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Golduck
pokedexEntry: Golduck is the fastest swimmer among all Pokemon. It swims effortlessly, even in a rough, stormy sea. It sometimes rescues people from wrecked ships floundering in high seas.

description:
Pokemon GO Mankey is a fighting type with 1002 MAX CP.
Mankey best moveset is Karate Chop and Cross Chop.
Mankey is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Mankey is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Mankey
pokedexEntry: When Mankey starts shaking and its nasal breathing turns rough, it's a sure sign that it is becoming angry. However, because it goes into a towering rage almost instantly, it is impossible for anyone to flee its wrath.

description:
Pokemon GO Primeape is a fighting type with 2105 MAX CP.
Primeape best moveset is Karate Chop and Close Combat.
Primeape is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Primeape is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Primeape
pokedexEntry: When Primeape becomes furious, its blood circulation is boosted. In turn, its muscles are made even stronger. However, it also becomes much less intelligent at the same time.

description:
Pokemon GO Growlithe is a fire type with 1110 MAX CP.
Growlithe best moveset is Ember and Flamethrower.
Growlithe is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Growlithe is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Growlithe
pokedexEntry: Growlithe has a superb sense of smell. Once it smells anything, this Pokemon won't forget the scent, no matter what. It uses its advanced olfactory sense to determine the emotions of other living things.

description:
Pokemon GO Arcanine is a fire type with 2839 MAX CP.
Arcanine best moveset is Fire Fang and Fire Blast.
Arcanine is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Arcanine is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Arcanine
pokedexEntry: Arcanine is known for its high speed. It is said to be capable of running over 6,200 miles in a single day and night. The fire that blazes wildly within this Pokemon's body is its source of power.

description:
Pokemon GO Poliwag is a water type with 695 MAX CP.
Poliwag best moveset is Bubble and Bubble Beam.
Poliwag is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Poliwag is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Poliwag
pokedexEntry: Poliwag has a very thin skin. It is possible to see the Pokemon's spiral innards right through the skin. Despite its thinness, however, the skin is also very flexible. Even sharp fangs bounce right off it.

description:
Pokemon GO Poliwhirl is a water type with 1313 MAX CP.
Poliwhirl best moveset is Bubble and Water Pulse.
Poliwhirl is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Poliwhirl is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Poliwhirl
pokedexEntry: The surface of Poliwhirl's body is always wet and slick with a slimy fluid. Because of this slippery covering, it can easily slip and slide out of the clutches of any enemy in battle.

description:
Pokemon GO Poliwrath is a water fighting type with 2441 MAX CP.
Poliwrath best moveset is Bubble and Dynamic Punch.
Poliwrath is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Poliwrath is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
name: Poliwrath
pokedexEntry: Poliwrath's highly developed, brawny muscles never grow fatigued, however much it exercises. It is so tirelessly strong, this Pokemon can swim back and forth across the ocean without effort.

description:
Pokemon GO Abra is a psychic type with 1148 MAX CP.
Abra best moveset is Zen Headbutt and Psyshock.
Abra is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Abra is boosted by Wind weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Abra
pokedexEntry: Abra needs to sleep for eighteen hours a day. If it doesn't, this Pokemon loses its ability to use telekinetic powers. If it is attacked, Abra escapes using Teleport while it is still sleeping.

description:
Pokemon GO Kadabra is a psychic type with 1859 MAX CP.
Kadabra best moveset is Confusion and Shadow Ball.
Kadabra is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Kadabra is boosted by Wind weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Kadabra
pokedexEntry: Kadabra holds a silver spoon in its hand. The spoon is used to amplify the alpha waves in its brain. Without the spoon, the Pokemon is said to be limited to half the usual amount of its telekinetic powers.

description:
Pokemon GO Alakazam is a psychic type with 2887 MAX CP.
Alakazam best moveset is Psycho Cut and Futuresight.
Alakazam is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Alakazam is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Alakazam
pokedexEntry: Alakazam's brain continually grows, infinitely multiplying brain cells. This amazing brain gives this Pokemon an astoundingly high IQ of 5,000. It has a thorough memory of everything that has occurred in the world.

description:
Pokemon GO Machop is a fighting type with 1199 MAX CP.
Machop best moveset is Karate Chop and Cross Chop.
Machop is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Machop is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Machop
pokedexEntry: Machop exercises by hefting around a Graveler as if it were a barbell. There are some Machop that travel the world in a quest to master all kinds of martial arts.

description:
Pokemon GO Machoke is a fighting type with 1910 MAX CP.
Machoke best moveset is Karate Chop and Dynamic Punch.
Machoke is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Machoke is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Machoke
pokedexEntry: Machoke undertakes bodybuilding every day even as it helps people with tough, physically demanding labor. On its days off, this Pokemon heads to the fields and mountains to exercise and train.

description:
Pokemon GO Machamp is a fighting type with 2889 MAX CP.
Machamp best moveset is Counter and Dynamic Punch.
Machamp is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Machamp is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Machamp
pokedexEntry: Machamp is known as the Pokemon that has mastered every kind of martial arts. If it grabs hold of the foe with its four arms, the battle is all but over. The hapless foe is thrown far over the horizon.

description:
Pokemon GO Bellsprout is a grass poison type with 916 MAX CP.
Bellsprout best moveset is Vine Whip and Power Whip.
Bellsprout is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Psychic type moves.
Bellsprout is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Bellsprout
pokedexEntry: Bellsprout's thin and flexible body lets it bend and sway to avoid any attack, however strong it may be. From its mouth, this Pokemon spits a corrosive fluid that melts even iron.

description:
Pokemon GO Weepinbell is a grass poison type with 1475 MAX CP.
Weepinbell best moveset is Acid and Power Whip.
Weepinbell is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Psychic type moves.
Weepinbell is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Weepinbell
pokedexEntry: Weepinbell has a large hook on its rear end. At night, the Pokemon hooks on to a tree branch and goes to sleep. If it moves around in its sleep, it may wake up to find itself on the ground.

description:
Pokemon GO Victreebel is a grass poison type with 2268 MAX CP.
Victreebel best moveset is Acid and Solar Beam.
Victreebel is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Psychic type moves.
Victreebel is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
name: Victreebel
pokedexEntry: Victreebel has a long vine that extends from its head. This vine is waved and flicked about as if it were an animal to attract prey. When an unsuspecting prey draws near, this Pokemon swallows it whole.

description:
Pokemon GO Tentacool is a water poison type with 956 MAX CP.
Tentacool best moveset is Poison Sting and Bubble Beam.
Tentacool is vulnerable to Electric, Ground, Psychic type moves.
Tentacool is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Tentacool
pokedexEntry: Tentacool absorbs sunlight and refracts it using water inside its body to convert it into beam energy. This Pokemon shoots beams from the small round organ above its eyes.

description:
Pokemon GO Tentacruel is a water poison type with 2374 MAX CP.
Tentacruel best moveset is Poison Jab and Hydro Pump.
Tentacruel is vulnerable to Electric, Ground, Psychic type moves.
Tentacruel is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
name: Tentacruel
pokedexEntry: Tentacruel has tentacles that can be freely elongated and shortened at will. It ensnares prey with its tentacles and weakens the prey by dosing it with a harsh toxin. It can catch up to 80 prey at the same time.

description:
Pokemon GO Geodude is a rock ground type with 1193 MAX CP.
Geodude best moveset is Rock Throw and Rock Slide.
Geodude is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Steel, Water, Ice type moves.
Geodude is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Clear
name: Geodude
pokedexEntry: When Geodude sleeps deeply, it buries itself halfway into the ground. It will not awaken even if hikers step on it unwittingly. In the morning, this Pokemon rolls downhill in search of food.

description:
Pokemon GO Graveler is a rock ground type with 1815 MAX CP.
Graveler best moveset is Rock Throw and Stone Edge.
Graveler is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Steel, Water, Ice type moves.
Graveler is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Clear
name: Graveler
pokedexEntry: Rocks are Graveler's favorite food. This Pokemon will climb a mountain from the base to the summit, crunchingly feasting on rocks all the while. Upon reaching the peak, it rolls back down to the bottom.

description:
Pokemon GO Golem is a rock ground type with 2916 MAX CP.
Golem best moveset is Rock Throw and Stone Edge.
Golem is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Steel, Water, Ice type moves.
Golem is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Clear
name: Golem
pokedexEntry: Golem is known for rolling down from mountains. To prevent them from rolling into the homes of people downhill, grooves have been dug into the sides of mountains to serve as guideways for diverting this Pokemon's course.

description:
Pokemon GO Ponyta is a fire type with 1502 MAX CP.
Ponyta best moveset is Ember and Fire Blast.
Ponyta is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Ponyta is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Ponyta
pokedexEntry: Ponyta is very weak at birth. It can barely stand up. This Pokemon becomes stronger by stumbling and falling to keep up with its parent.

description:
Pokemon GO Rapidash is a fire type with 2252 MAX CP.
Rapidash best moveset is Fire Spin and Fire Blast.
Rapidash is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Rapidash is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Rapidash
pokedexEntry: Rapidash usually can be seen casually cantering in the fields and plains. However, when this Pokemon turns serious, its fiery manes flare and blaze as it gallops its way up to 150 mph.

description:
Pokemon GO Slowpoke is a water psychic type with 1204 MAX CP.
Slowpoke best moveset is Confusion and Psyshock.
Slowpoke is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Slowpoke is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Slowpoke
pokedexEntry: Slowpoke uses its tail to catch prey by dipping it in water at the side of a river. However, this Pokemon often forgets what it's doing and often spends entire days just loafing at water's edge.

description:
Pokemon GO Slowbro is a water psychic type with 2482 MAX CP.
Slowbro best moveset is Confusion and Psychic.
Slowbro is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Slowbro is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Slowbro
pokedexEntry: Slowbro's tail has a Shellder firmly attached with a bite. As a result, the tail can't be used for fishing anymore. This causes Slowbro to grudgingly swim and catch prey instead.

description:
Pokemon GO Magnemite is a electric steel type with 1083 MAX CP.
Magnemite best moveset is Spark and Thunderbolt.
Magnemite is vulnerable to Ground, Fighting, Fire type moves.
Magnemite is boosted by Rain and Snow weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Magnemite
pokedexEntry: Magnemite floats in the air by emitting electromagnetic waves from the units at its sides. These waves block gravity. This Pokemon becomes incapable of flight if its internal electrical supply is depleted.

description:
Pokemon GO Magneton is a electric steel type with 2237 MAX CP.
Magneton best moveset is Thunder Shock and Zap Cannon.
Magneton is vulnerable to Ground, Fighting, Fire type moves.
Magneton is boosted by Rain and Snow weather.
name: Magneton
pokedexEntry: Magneton emits a powerful magnetic force that is fatal to electronics and precision instruments. Because of this, it is said that some towns warn people to keep this Pokemon inside a Poke Ball.

description:
Pokemon GO Farfetch'd is a normal flying type with 1092 MAX CP.
Farfetch'd best moveset is Air Slash and Aerial Ace.
Farfetch'd is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Farfetch'd is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
name: Farfetch'd
pokedexEntry: Farfetch'd is always seen with a stalk from a plant of some sort. Apparently, there are good stalks and bad stalks. This Pokemon has been known to fight with others over stalks.

description:
Pokemon GO Doduo is a normal flying type with 1011 MAX CP.
Doduo best moveset is Quick Attack and Drill Peck.
Doduo is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Doduo is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Doduo
pokedexEntry: Doduo's two heads contain completely identical brains. A scientific study reported that on rare occasions, there will be examples of this Pokemon possessing different sets of brains.

description:
Pokemon GO Dodrio is a normal flying type with 2138 MAX CP.
Dodrio best moveset is Feint Attack and Drill Peck.
Dodrio is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Dodrio is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
name: Dodrio
pokedexEntry: Apparently, the heads aren't the only parts of the body that Dodrio has three of. It has three sets of hearts and lungs as well, so it is capable of running long distances without rest.

description:
Pokemon GO Seel is a water type with 899 MAX CP.
Seel best moveset is Lick and Aqua Tail.
Seel is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Seel is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Seel
pokedexEntry: Seel hunts for prey in the frigid sea underneath sheets of ice. When it needs to breathe, it punches a hole through the ice with the sharply protruding section of its head.

description:
Pokemon GO Dewgong is a water ice type with 1894 MAX CP.
Dewgong best moveset is Frost Breath and Blizzard.
Dewgong is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Fighting, Rock type moves.
Dewgong is boosted by Rain and Snow weather.
name: Dewgong
pokedexEntry: Dewgong loves to snooze on bitterly cold ice. The sight of this Pokemon sleeping on a glacier was mistakenly thought to be a mermaid by a mariner long ago.

description:
Pokemon GO Grimer is a poison type with 1269 MAX CP.
Grimer best moveset is Poison Jab and Sludge Bomb.
Grimer is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Grimer is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Grimer
pokedexEntry: Grimer emerged from the sludge that settled on a polluted seabed. This Pokemon loves anything filthy. It constantly leaks a horribly germ-infested fluid from all over its body.

description:
Pokemon GO Muk is a poison type with 2709 MAX CP.
Muk best moveset is Poison Jab and Gunk Shot.
Muk is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Muk is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Muk
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon's favorite food is anything that is repugnantly filthy. In dirty towns where people think nothing of throwing away litter on the streets, Muk are certain to gather.

description:
Pokemon GO Shellder is a water type with 958 MAX CP.
Shellder best moveset is Tackle and Bubble Beam.
Shellder is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Shellder is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Shellder
pokedexEntry: At night, this Pokemon uses its broad tongue to burrow a hole in the seafloor sand and then sleep in it. While it is sleeping, Shellder closes its shell, but leaves its tongue hanging out.

description:
Pokemon GO Cloyster is a water ice type with 2475 MAX CP.
Cloyster best moveset is Ice Shard and Avalanche.
Cloyster is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Fighting, Rock type moves.
Cloyster is boosted by Rain and Snow weather.
name: Cloyster
pokedexEntry: Cloyster is capable of swimming in the sea. It does so by swallowing water, then jetting it out toward the rear. This Pokemon shoots spikes from its shell using the same system.

description:
Pokemon GO Gastly is a ghost poison type with 1002 MAX CP.
Gastly best moveset is Lick and Sludge Bomb.
Gastly is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost, Ground, Psychic type moves.
Gastly is boosted by Fog and Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Gastly
pokedexEntry: Gastly is largely composed of gaseous matter. When exposed to a strong wind, the gaseous body quickly dwindles away. Groups of this Pokemon cluster under the eaves of houses to escape the ravages of wind.

description:
Pokemon GO Haunter is a ghost poison type with 1716 MAX CP.
Haunter best moveset is Shadow Claw and Shadow Ball.
Haunter is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost, Ground, Psychic type moves.
Haunter is boosted by Fog and Cloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Haunter
pokedexEntry: Haunter is a dangerous Pokemon. If one beckons you while floating in darkness, you must never approach it. This Pokemon will try to lick you with its tongue and steal your life away.

description:
Pokemon GO Gengar is a ghost poison type with 2619 MAX CP.
Gengar best moveset is Shadow Claw and Shadow Ball.
Gengar is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost, Ground, Psychic type moves.
Gengar is boosted by Fog and Cloudy weather.
name: Gengar
pokedexEntry: Sometimes, on a dark night, your shadow thrown by a streetlight will suddenly and startlingly overtake you. It is actually a Gengar running past you, pretending to be your shadow.

description:
Pokemon GO Onix is a rock ground type with 1002 MAX CP.
Onix best moveset is Rock Throw and Stone Edge.
Onix is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Steel, Water, Ice type moves.
Onix is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Clear
name: Onix
pokedexEntry: Onix has a magnet in its brain. It acts as a compass so that this Pokemon does not lose direction while it is tunneling. As it grows older, its body becomes increasingly rounder and smoother.

description:
Pokemon GO Drowzee is a psychic type with 992 MAX CP.
Drowzee best moveset is Confusion and Psyshock.
Drowzee is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Drowzee is boosted by Wind weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Drowzee
pokedexEntry: If your nose becomes itchy while you are sleeping, it's a sure sign that one of these Pokemon is standing above your pillow and trying to eat your dream through your nostrils.

description:
Pokemon GO Hypno is a psychic type with 2048 MAX CP.
Hypno best moveset is Confusion and Futuresight.
Hypno is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Hypno is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Hypno
pokedexEntry: Hypno holds a pendulum in its hand. The arcing movement and glitter of the pendulum lull the foe into a deep state of hypnosis. While this Pokemon searches for prey, it polishes the pendulum.

description:
Pokemon GO Krabby is a water type with 1386 MAX CP.
Krabby best moveset is Bubble and Bubble Beam.
Krabby is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Krabby is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Krabby
pokedexEntry: Krabby live on beaches, burrowed inside holes dug into the sand. On sandy beaches with little in the way of food, these Pokemon can be seen squabbling with each other over territory.

description:
Pokemon GO Kingler is a water type with 2694 MAX CP.
Kingler best moveset is Bubble and Water Pulse.
Kingler is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Kingler is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Kingler
pokedexEntry: Kingler has an enormous, oversized claw. It waves this huge claw in the air to communicate with others. However, because the claw is so heavy, the Pokemon quickly tires.

description:
Pokemon GO Voltorb is a electric type with 857 MAX CP.
Voltorb best moveset is Spark and Thunderbolt.
Voltorb is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Voltorb is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Voltorb
pokedexEntry: Voltorb is extremely sensitive—it explodes at the slightest of shocks. It is rumored that it was first created when a Poke Ball was exposed to a powerful pulse of energy.

description:
Pokemon GO Electrode is a electric type with 1900 MAX CP.
Electrode best moveset is Spark and Discharge.
Electrode is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Electrode is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Electrode
pokedexEntry: One of Electrode's characteristics is its attraction to electricity. It is a problematical Pokemon that congregates mostly at electrical power plants to feed on electricity that has just been generated.

description:
Pokemon GO Exeggcute is a grass psychic type with 1102 MAX CP.
Exeggcute best moveset is Confusion and Seed Bomb.
Exeggcute is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Exeggcute is boosted by
name: Exeggcute
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon consists of six eggs that form a closely knit cluster. The six eggs attract each other and spin around. When cracks increasingly appear on the eggs, Exeggcute is close to evolution.

description:
Pokemon GO Exeggutor is a grass psychic type with 2916 MAX CP.
Exeggutor best moveset is Confusion and Solar Beam.
Exeggutor is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Exeggutor is boosted by
name: Exeggutor
pokedexEntry: Exeggutor originally came from the tropics. Its heads steadily grow larger from exposure to strong sunlight. It is said that when the heads fall off, they group together to form Exeggcute.

description:
Pokemon GO Cubone is a ground type with 943 MAX CP.
Cubone best moveset is Mud Slap and Dig.
Cubone is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water type moves.
Cubone is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Cubone
pokedexEntry: Cubone pines for the mother it will never see again. Seeing a likeness of its mother in the full moon, it cries. The stains on the skull the Pokemon wears are made by the tears it sheds.

description:
Pokemon GO Marowak is a ground type with 1691 MAX CP.
Marowak best moveset is Mud Slap and Earthquake.
Marowak is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water type moves.
Marowak is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Marowak
pokedexEntry: Marowak is the evolved form of a Cubone that has overcome its sadness at the loss of its mother and grown tough. This Pokemon's tempered and hardened spirit is not easily broken.

description:
Pokemon GO Hitmonlee is a fighting type with 2406 MAX CP.
Hitmonlee best moveset is Low Kick and Close Combat.
Hitmonlee is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Hitmonlee is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Hitmonlee
pokedexEntry: Hitmonlee's legs freely contract and stretch. Using these springlike legs, it bowls over foes with devastating kicks. After battle, it rubs down its legs and loosens the muscles to overcome fatigue.

description:
Pokemon GO Hitmonchan is a fighting type with 2098 MAX CP.
Hitmonchan best moveset is Counter and Close Combat.
Hitmonchan is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Hitmonchan is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Hitmonchan
pokedexEntry: Hitmonchan is said to possess the spirit of a boxer who had been working toward a world championship. This Pokemon has an indomitable spirit and will never give up in the face of adversity.

description:
Pokemon GO Lickitung is a normal type with 1322 MAX CP.
Lickitung best moveset is Lick and Hyper Beam.
Lickitung is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Lickitung is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Lickitung
pokedexEntry: Whenever Lickitung comes across something new, it will unfailingly give it a lick. It does so because it memorizes things by texture and by taste. It is somewhat put off by sour things.

description:
Pokemon GO Koffing is a poison type with 1091 MAX CP.
Koffing best moveset is Acid and Sludge Bomb.
Koffing is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Koffing is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Koffing
pokedexEntry: Koffing embodies toxic substances. It mixes the toxins with raw garbage to set off a chemical reaction that results in a terribly powerful poison gas. The higher the temperature, the more gas is concocted by this Pokemon.

description:
Pokemon GO Weezing is a poison type with 2183 MAX CP.
Weezing best moveset is Acid and Sludge Bomb.
Weezing is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Weezing is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Weezing
pokedexEntry: Weezing alternately shrinks and inflates its twin bodies to mix together toxic gases inside. The more the gases are mixed, the more powerful the toxins become. The Pokemon also becomes more putrid.

description:
Pokemon GO Rhyhorn is a ground rock type with 1679 MAX CP.
Rhyhorn best moveset is Mud Slap and Bulldoze.
Rhyhorn is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water, Fighting, Ground, Steel type moves.
Rhyhorn is boosted by Clear and PartlyCloudy
name: Rhyhorn
pokedexEntry: Rhyhorn's brain is very small. It is so dense, while on a run it forgets why it started running in the first place. It apparently remembers sometimes if it demolishes something.

description:
Pokemon GO Rhydon is a ground rock type with 3300 MAX CP.
Rhydon best moveset is Mud Slap and Earthquake.
Rhydon is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water, Fighting, Ground, Steel type moves.
Rhydon is boosted by Clear and PartlyCloudy
name: Rhydon
pokedexEntry: Rhydon has a horn that serves as a drill. It is used for destroying rocks and boulders. This Pokemon occasionally rams into streams of magma, but the armor-like hide prevents it from feeling the heat.

description:
Pokemon GO Chansey is a normal type with 1469 MAX CP.
Chansey best moveset is Pound and Hyper Beam.
Chansey is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Chansey is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Chansey
pokedexEntry: Chansey lays nutritionally excellent eggs on an everyday basis. The eggs are so delicious, they are easily and eagerly devoured by even those people who have lost their appetite.

description:
Pokemon GO Tangela is a grass type with 2208 MAX CP.
Tangela best moveset is Vine Whip and Solar Beam.
Tangela is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Tangela is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Tangela
pokedexEntry: Tangela's vines snap off easily if they are grabbed. This happens without pain, allowing it to make a quick getaway. The lost vines are replaced by newly grown vines the very next day.

description:
Pokemon GO Kangaskhan is a normal type with 2463 MAX CP.
Kangaskhan best moveset is Low Kick and Outrage.
Kangaskhan is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Kangaskhan is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Kangaskhan
pokedexEntry: If you come across a young Kangaskhan playing by itself, you must never disturb it or attempt to catch it. The baby Pokemon's parent is sure to be in the area, and it will become violently enraged at you.

description:
Pokemon GO Horsea is a water type with 921 MAX CP.
Horsea best moveset is Water Gun and Bubble Beam.
Horsea is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Horsea is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Horsea
pokedexEntry: If Horsea senses danger, it will reflexively spray a dense black ink from its mouth and try to escape. This Pokemon swims by cleverly flapping the fin on its back.

description:
Pokemon GO Seadra is a water type with 1979 MAX CP.
Seadra best moveset is Dragon Breath and Hydro Pump.
Seadra is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Seadra is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Seadra
pokedexEntry: Seadra generates whirlpools by spinning its body. The whirlpools are strong enough to swallow even fishing boats. This Pokemon weakens prey with these currents, then swallows it whole.

description:
Pokemon GO Goldeen is a water type with 1006 MAX CP.
Goldeen best moveset is Mud Shot and Aqua Tail.
Goldeen is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Goldeen is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Goldeen
pokedexEntry: Goldeen loves swimming wild and free in rivers and ponds. If one of these Pokemon is placed in an aquarium, it will shatter even the thickest glass with one ram of its horn and make its escape.

description:
Pokemon GO Seaking is a water type with 2040 MAX CP.
Seaking best moveset is Waterfall and Drill Run.
Seaking is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Seaking is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Seaking
pokedexEntry: Seaking is very protective of its eggs. The male and female will take turns patrolling around their nest and eggs. The guarding of eggs by these Pokemon goes on for over a month.

description:
Pokemon GO Staryu is a water type with 926 MAX CP.
Staryu best moveset is Water Gun and Bubble Beam.
Staryu is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Staryu is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Staryu
pokedexEntry: Staryu apparently communicates with the stars in the night sky by flashing the red core at the center of its body. If parts of its body are torn, this Pokemon simply regenerates the missing pieces and limbs.

description:
Pokemon GO Starmie is a water psychic type with 2303 MAX CP.
Starmie best moveset is Quick Attack and Hydro Pump.
Starmie is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Starmie is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Starmie
pokedexEntry: Starmie swims through water by spinning its star-shaped body as if it were a propeller on a ship. The core at the center of this Pokemon's body glows in seven colors.

description:
Pokemon GO Mr.
Mime is a psychic fairy type with 1984 MAX CP.
Mr.
Mime best moveset is Confusion and Shadow Ball.
Mr.
Mime is vulnerable to Ghost, Poison, Steel type moves.
Mr.
Mime is boosted by Wind and Cloudy weather.
name: Mr. Mime
pokedexEntry: Mr. Mime is a master of pantomime. Its gestures and motions convince watchers that something unseeable actually exists. Once the watchers are convinced, the unseeable thing exists as if it were real.

description:
Pokemon GO Scyther is a bug flying type with 2464 MAX CP.
Scyther best moveset is Fury Cutter and Bug Buzz.
Scyther is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Scyther is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Scyther
pokedexEntry: Scyther is blindingly fast. Its blazing speed enhances the effectiveness of the twin scythes on its forearms. This Pokemon's scythes are so effective, they can slice through thick logs in one wicked stroke.

description:
Pokemon GO Jynx is a ice psychic type with 2512 MAX CP.
Jynx best moveset is Confusion and Avalanche.
Jynx is vulnerable to Rock, Steel, Fire, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Jynx is boosted by Snow and Wind
name: Jynx
pokedexEntry: Jynx walks rhythmically, swaying and shaking its hips as if it were dancing. Its motions are so bouncingly alluring, people seeing it are compelled to shake their hips without giving any thought to what they are doing.

description:
Pokemon GO Electabuzz is a electric type with 2196 MAX CP.
Electabuzz best moveset is Thunder Shock and Thunderbolt.
Electabuzz is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Electabuzz is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Electabuzz
pokedexEntry: When a storm arrives, gangs of this Pokemon compete with each other to scale heights that are likely to be stricken by lightning bolts. Some towns use Electabuzz in place of lightning rods.

description:
Pokemon GO Magmar is a fire type with 2254 MAX CP.
Magmar best moveset is Karate Chop and Flamethrower.
Magmar is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Magmar is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Magmar
pokedexEntry: In battle, Magmar blows out intensely hot flames from all over its body to intimidate its opponent. This Pokemon's fiery bursts create heat waves that ignite grass and trees in its surroundings.

description:
Pokemon GO Pinsir is a bug type with 2770 MAX CP.
Pinsir best moveset is Bug Bite and X Scissor.
Pinsir is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock type moves.
Pinsir is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Pinsir
pokedexEntry: Pinsir has a pair of massive horns. Protruding from the surface of these horns are thorns. These thorns are driven deeply into the foe's body when the pincer closes, making it tough for the foe to escape.

description:
Pokemon GO Tauros is a normal type with 2488 MAX CP.
Tauros best moveset is Tackle and Horn Attack.
Tauros is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Tauros is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Tauros
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon is not satisfied unless it is rampaging at all times. If there is no opponent for Tauros to battle, it will charge at thick trees and knock them down to calm itself.

description:
Pokemon GO Magikarp is a water type with 220 MAX CP.
Magikarp best moveset is Splash and Struggle.
Magikarp is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Magikarp is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 400 candy to evolve!
name: Magikarp
pokedexEntry: Magikarp is virtually useless in battle as it can only splash around. As a result, it is considered to be weak. However, it is actually a very hardy Pokemon that can survive in any body of water no matter how polluted it is.

description:
Pokemon GO Gyarados is a water flying type with 3281 MAX CP.
Gyarados best moveset is Dragon Tail and Hydro Pump.
Gyarados is vulnerable to Electric, Rock type moves.
Gyarados is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Gyarados
pokedexEntry: Once Gyarados goes on a rampage, its ferociously violent blood doesn't calm until it has burned everything down. There are records of this Pokemon's rampages lasting a whole month.

description:
Pokemon GO Lapras is a water ice type with 2603 MAX CP.
Lapras best moveset is Water Gun and Surf.
Lapras is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Fighting, Rock type moves.
Lapras is boosted by Rain and Snow weather.
name: Lapras
pokedexEntry: People have driven Lapras almost to the point of extinction. In the evenings, this Pokemon is said to sing plaintively as it seeks what few others of its kind still remain.

description:
Pokemon GO Ditto is a normal type with 718 MAX CP.
Ditto best moveset is Transform and Struggle.
Ditto is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Ditto is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Ditto
pokedexEntry: Ditto rearranges its cell structure to transform itself into other shapes. However, if it tries to transform itself into something by relying on its memory, this Pokemon manages to get details wrong.

description:
Pokemon GO Eevee is a normal type with 969 MAX CP.
Eevee best moveset is Quick Attack and Body Slam.
Eevee is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Eevee is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Eevee
pokedexEntry: Eevee has an unstable genetic makeup that suddenly mutates due to the environment in which it lives. Radiation from various stones causes this Pokemon to evolve.

description:
Pokemon GO Vaporeon is a water type with 3157 MAX CP.
Vaporeon best moveset is Water Gun and Hydro Pump.
Vaporeon is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Vaporeon is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Vaporeon
pokedexEntry: Vaporeon underwent a spontaneous mutation and grew fins and gills that allow it to live underwater. This Pokemon has the ability to freely control water.

description:
Pokemon GO Jolteon is a electric type with 2730 MAX CP.
Jolteon best moveset is Thunder Shock and Thunderbolt.
Jolteon is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Jolteon is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Jolteon
pokedexEntry: Jolteon's cells generate a low level of electricity. This power is amplified by the static electricity of its fur, enabling the Pokemon to drop thunderbolts. The bristling fur is made of electrically charged needles.

description:
Pokemon GO Flareon is a fire type with 2904 MAX CP.
Flareon best moveset is Fire Spin and Overheat.
Flareon is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Flareon is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Flareon
pokedexEntry: Flareon's fluffy fur has a functional purpose—it releases heat into the air so that its body does not get excessively hot. This Pokemon's body temperature can rise to a maximum of 1,650 degrees Fahrenheit.

description:
Pokemon GO Porygon is a normal type with 1567 MAX CP.
Porygon best moveset is Quick Attack and Hyper Beam.
Porygon is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Porygon is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Porygon
pokedexEntry: Porygon is capable of reverting itself entirely back to program data and entering cyberspace. This Pokemon is copy protected so it cannot be duplicated by copying.

description:
Pokemon GO Omanyte is a rock water type with 1345 MAX CP.
Omanyte best moveset is Water Gun and Ancient Power.
Omanyte is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Electric type moves.
Omanyte is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Omanyte
pokedexEntry: Omanyte is one of the ancient and long-since-extinct Pokemon that have been regenerated from fossils by people. If attacked by an enemy, it withdraws itself inside its hard shell.

description:
Pokemon GO Omastar is a rock water type with 2685 MAX CP.
Omastar best moveset is Rock Throw and Rock Slide.
Omastar is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Electric type moves.
Omastar is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Rain weather.
name: Omastar
pokedexEntry: Omastar uses its tentacles to capture its prey. It is believed to have become extinct because its shell grew too large and heavy, causing its movements to become too slow and ponderous.

description:
Pokemon GO Kabuto is a rock water type with 1172 MAX CP.
Kabuto best moveset is Scratch and Ancient Power.
Kabuto is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Electric type moves.
Kabuto is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Kabuto
pokedexEntry: Kabuto is a Pokemon that has been regenerated from a fossil. However, in extremely rare cases, living examples have been discovered. The Pokemon has not changed at all for 300 million years.

description:
Pokemon GO Kabutops is a rock water type with 2517 MAX CP.
Kabutops best moveset is Fury Cutter and Ancient Power.
Kabutops is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Electric type moves.
Kabutops is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Rain weather.
name: Kabutops
pokedexEntry: Kabutops swam underwater to hunt for its prey in ancient times. The Pokemon was apparently evolving from being a water dweller to living on land as evident from the beginnings of change in its gills and legs.

description:
Pokemon GO Aerodactyl is a rock flying type with 2608 MAX CP.
Aerodactyl best moveset is Steel Wing and Ancient Power.
Aerodactyl is vulnerable to Steel, Water, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Aerodactyl is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
name: Aerodactyl
pokedexEntry: Aerodactyl is a Pokemon from the age of dinosaurs. It was regenerated from genetic material extracted from amber. It is imagined to have been the king of the skies in ancient times.

description:
Pokemon GO Snorlax is a normal type with 3355 MAX CP.
Snorlax best moveset is Lick and Hyper Beam.
Snorlax is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Snorlax is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Snorlax
pokedexEntry: Snorlax's typical day consists of nothing more than eating and sleeping. It is such a docile Pokemon that there are children who use its expansive belly as a place to play.

description:
Pokemon GO Articuno is a ice flying type with 2933 MAX CP.
Articuno best moveset is Frost Breath and Ice Beam.
Articuno is vulnerable to Rock, Steel, Fire, Electric type moves.
Articuno is boosted by Snow and Wind weather.
name: Articuno
pokedexEntry: Articuno is a legendary bird Pokemon that can control ice. The flapping of its wings chills the air. As a result, it is said that when this Pokemon flies, snow will fall.

description:
Pokemon GO Zapdos is a electric flying type with 3330 MAX CP.
Zapdos best moveset is Charge Beam and Thunderbolt.
Zapdos is vulnerable to Rock, Ice type moves.
Zapdos is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Zapdos
pokedexEntry: Zapdos is a legendary bird Pokemon that has the ability to control electricity. It usually lives in thunderclouds. The Pokemon gains power if it is stricken by lightning bolts.

description:
Pokemon GO Moltres is a fire flying type with 3272 MAX CP.
Moltres best moveset is Fire Spin and Overheat.
Moltres is vulnerable to Rock, Water, Electric type moves.
Moltres is boosted by Clear and Wind weather.
name: Moltres
pokedexEntry: Moltres is a legendary bird Pokemon that has the ability to control fire. If this Pokemon is injured, it is said to dip its body in the molten magma of a volcano to burn and heal itself.

description:
Pokemon GO Dratini is a dragon type with 860 MAX CP.
Dratini best moveset is Dragon Breath and Aqua Tail.
Dratini is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy type moves.
Dratini is boosted by Wind weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Dratini
pokedexEntry: Dratini continually molts and sloughs off its old skin. It does so because the life energy within its body steadily builds to reach uncontrollable levels.

description:
Pokemon GO Dragonair is a dragon type with 1609 MAX CP.
Dragonair best moveset is Dragon Breath and Dragon Pulse.
Dragonair is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy type moves.
Dragonair is boosted by Wind weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Dragonair
pokedexEntry: Dragonair stores an enormous amount of energy inside its body. It is said to alter weather conditions in its vicinity by discharging energy from the crystals on its neck and tail.

description:
Pokemon GO Dragonite is a dragon flying type with 3581 MAX CP.
Dragonite best moveset is Dragon Tail and Outrage.
Dragonite is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy, Rock type moves.
Dragonite is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Dragonite
pokedexEntry: Dragonite is capable of circling the globe in just 16 hours. It is a kindhearted Pokemon that leads lost and foundering ships in a storm to the safety of land.

description:
Pokemon GO Mewtwo is a psychic type with 3982 MAX CP.
Mewtwo best moveset is Confusion and Shadow Ball.
Mewtwo is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Mewtwo is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Mewtwo
pokedexEntry: Mewtwo is a Pokemon that was created by genetic manipulation. However, even though the scientific power of humans created this Pokemon's body, they failed to endow Mewtwo with a compassionate heart.

description:
Pokemon GO Mew is a psychic type with 3090 MAX CP.
Mew best moveset is Pound and Solar Beam.
Mew is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Mew is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Mew
pokedexEntry: Mew is said to possess the genetic composition of all Pokemon. It is capable of making itself invisible at will, so it entirely avoids notice even if it approaches people.

description:
Pokemon GO Chikorita is a grass type with 801 MAX CP.
Chikorita best moveset is Vine Whip and Grass Knot.
Chikorita is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Chikorita is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Chikorita
pokedexEntry: In battle, Chikorita waves its leaf around to keep the foe at bay. However, a sweet fragrance also wafts from the leaf, becalming the battling Pokemon and creating a cozy, friendly atmosphere all around.

description:
Pokemon GO Bayleef is a grass type with 1296 MAX CP.
Bayleef best moveset is Tackle and Grass Knot.
Bayleef is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Bayleef is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Bayleef
pokedexEntry: Bayleef's neck is ringed by curled-up leaves. Inside each tubular leaf is a small shoot of a tree. The fragrance of this shoot makes people peppy.

description:
Pokemon GO Meganium is a grass type with 2227 MAX CP.
Meganium best moveset is Vine Whip and Solar Beam.
Meganium is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Meganium is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Meganium
pokedexEntry: The fragrance of Meganium's flower soothes and calms emotions. In battle, this Pokemon gives off more of its becalming scent to blunt the foe's fighting spirit.

description:
Pokemon GO Cyndaquil is a fire type with 831 MAX CP.
Cyndaquil best moveset is Ember and Flamethrower.
Cyndaquil is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Cyndaquil is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Cyndaquil
pokedexEntry: Cyndaquil protects itself by flaring up the flames on its back. The flames are vigorous if the Pokemon is angry. However, if it is tired, the flames splutter fitfully with incomplete combustion.

description:
Pokemon GO Quilava is a fire type with 1484 MAX CP.
Quilava best moveset is Ember and Flamethrower.
Quilava is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Quilava is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Quilava
pokedexEntry: Quilava keeps its foes at bay with the intensity of its flames and gusts of superheated air. This Pokemon applies its outstanding nimbleness to dodge attacks even while scorching the foe with flames.

description:
Pokemon GO Typhlosion is a fire type with 2686 MAX CP.
Typhlosion best moveset is Shadow Claw and Overheat.
Typhlosion is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Typhlosion is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Typhlosion
pokedexEntry: Typhlosion obscures itself behind a shimmering heat haze that it creates using its intensely hot flames. This Pokemon creates blazing explosive blasts that burn everything to cinders.

description:
Pokemon GO Totodile is a water type with 1011 MAX CP.
Totodile best moveset is Water Gun and Water Pulse.
Totodile is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Totodile is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Totodile
pokedexEntry: Despite the smallness of its body, Totodile's jaws are very powerful. While the Pokemon may think it is just playfully nipping, its bite has enough power to cause serious injury.

description:
Pokemon GO Croconaw is a water type with 1598 MAX CP.
Croconaw best moveset is Water Gun and Water Pulse.
Croconaw is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Croconaw is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Croconaw
pokedexEntry: Once Croconaw has clamped its jaws on its foe, it will absolutely not let go. Because the tips of its fangs are forked back like barbed fishhooks, they become impossible to remove when they have sunk in.

description:
Pokemon GO Feraligatr is a water type with 2721 MAX CP.
Feraligatr best moveset is Waterfall and Hydro Pump.
Feraligatr is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Feraligatr is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Feraligatr
pokedexEntry: Feraligatr intimidates its foes by opening its huge mouth. In battle, it will kick the ground hard with its thick and powerful hind legs to charge at the foe at an incredible speed.

description:
Pokemon GO Sentret is a normal type with 519 MAX CP.
Sentret best moveset is Scratch and Grass Knot.
Sentret is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Sentret is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Sentret
pokedexEntry: When Sentret sleeps, it does so while another stands guard. The sentry wakes the others at the first sign of danger. When this Pokemon becomes separated from its pack, it becomes incapable of sleep due to fear.

description:
Pokemon GO Furret is a normal type with 1667 MAX CP.
Furret best moveset is Quick Attack and Hyper Beam.
Furret is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Furret is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Furret
pokedexEntry: Furret has a very slim build. When under attack, it can slickly squirm through narrow spaces and get away. In spite of its short limbs, this Pokemon is very nimble and fleet.

description:
Pokemon GO Hoothoot is a normal flying type with 640 MAX CP.
Hoothoot best moveset is Peck and Sky Attack.
Hoothoot is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Hoothoot is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Hoothoot
pokedexEntry: Hoothoot has an internal organ that senses and tracks the earth's rotation. Using this special organ, this Pokemon begins hooting at precisely the same time every day.

description:
Pokemon GO Noctowl is a normal flying type with 2040 MAX CP.
Noctowl best moveset is Wing Attack and Sky Attack.
Noctowl is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Noctowl is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
name: Noctowl
pokedexEntry: Noctowl never fails at catching prey in darkness. This Pokemon owes its success to its superior vision that allows it to see in minimal light, and to its soft, supple wings that make no sound in flight.

description:
Pokemon GO Ledyba is a bug flying type with 663 MAX CP.
Ledyba best moveset is Bug Bite and Aerial Ace.
Ledyba is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Ledyba is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Ledyba
pokedexEntry: Ledyba secretes an aromatic fluid from where its legs join its body. This fluid is used for communicating with others. This Pokemon conveys its feelings to others by altering the fluid's scent.

description:
Pokemon GO Ledian is a bug flying type with 1275 MAX CP.
Ledian best moveset is Bug Bite and Bug Buzz.
Ledian is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Ledian is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Ledian
pokedexEntry: It is said that in lands with clean air, where the stars fill the sky, there live Ledian in countless numbers. There is a good reason for this—the Pokemon uses the light of the stars as its energy.

description:
Pokemon GO Spinarak is a bug poison type with 685 MAX CP.
Spinarak best moveset is Bug Bite and Signal Beam.
Spinarak is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Psychic type moves.
Spinarak is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Spinarak
pokedexEntry: The web spun by Spinarak can be considered its second nervous system. It is said that this Pokemon can determine what kind of prey is touching its web just by the tiny vibrations it feels through the web's strands.

description:
Pokemon GO Ariados is a bug poison type with 1636 MAX CP.
Ariados best moveset is Infestation and Megahorn.
Ariados is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Psychic type moves.
Ariados is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
name: Ariados
pokedexEntry: Ariados's feet are tipped with tiny hooked claws that enable it to scuttle on ceilings and vertical walls. This Pokemon constricts the foe with thin and strong silk webbing.

description:
Pokemon GO Crobat is a poison flying type with 2466 MAX CP.
Crobat best moveset is Air Slash and Sludge Bomb.
Crobat is vulnerable to Psychic, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Crobat is boosted by Cloudy and Wind weather.
name: Crobat
pokedexEntry: Crobat sneaks up on its intended prey using wings that barely make a sound. This Pokemon rests by hanging on a tree branch with its rear legs that serve as wings.

description:
Pokemon GO Chinchou is a water electric type with 1067 MAX CP.
Chinchou best moveset is Bubble and Thunderbolt.
Chinchou is vulnerable to Grass, Ground type moves.
Chinchou is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Chinchou
pokedexEntry: Chinchou's two antennas are filled with cells that generate strong electricity. This Pokemon's cells create so much electrical power, it even makes itself tingle slightly.

description:
Pokemon GO Lanturn is a water electric type with 2077 MAX CP.
Lanturn best moveset is Charge Beam and Thunderbolt.
Lanturn is vulnerable to Grass, Ground type moves.
Lanturn is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Lanturn
pokedexEntry: Lanturn is known to emit light. If you peer down into the dark sea from a ship at night, you can sometimes see this Pokemon's light rising from the depths where it swims. It gives the sea an appearance of a starlit night.

description:
Pokemon GO Pichu is a electric type with 376 MAX CP.
Pichu best moveset is Thunder Shock and Thunderbolt.
Pichu is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Pichu is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Pichu
pokedexEntry: When Pichu plays with others, it may short out electricity with another Pichu, creating a shower of sparks. In that event, this Pokemon will begin crying, startled by the flash of sparks.

description:
Pokemon GO Cleffa is a fairy type with 620 MAX CP.
Cleffa best moveset is Pound and Grass Knot.
Cleffa is vulnerable to Poison, Steel type moves.
Cleffa is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Cleffa
pokedexEntry: On nights with many shooting stars, Cleffa can be seen dancing in a ring. They dance through the night and stop only at the break of day, when these Pokemon quench their thirst with the morning dew.

description:
Pokemon GO Igglybuff is a normal fairy type with 512 MAX CP.
Igglybuff best moveset is Pound and Wild Charge.
Igglybuff is vulnerable to Poison, Steel type moves.
Igglybuff is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Igglybuff
pokedexEntry: Igglybuff has a soft and plushy body that feels very much like a marshmallow. From this body wafts a gently sweet fragrance that soothes and calms the emotions of its foes.

description:
Pokemon GO Togepi is a fairy type with 540 MAX CP.
Togepi best moveset is Zen Headbutt and Dazzling Gleam.
Togepi is vulnerable to Poison, Steel type moves.
Togepi is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Togepi
pokedexEntry: As its energy, Togepi uses the positive emotions of compassion and pleasure exuded by people and Pokemon. This Pokemon stores up feelings of happiness inside its shell, then shares them with others.

description:
Pokemon GO Togetic is a fairy flying type with 1543 MAX CP.
Togetic best moveset is Zen Headbutt and Dazzling Gleam.
Togetic is vulnerable to Poison, Steel, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Togetic is boosted by Cloudy and Wind weather.
name: Togetic
pokedexEntry: Togetic is said to be a Pokemon that brings good fortune. When the Pokemon spots someone who is pure of heart, it is said to appear and share its happiness with that person.

description:
Pokemon GO Natu is a psychic flying type with 925 MAX CP.
Natu best moveset is Quick Attack and Drill Peck.
Natu is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Natu is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Natu
pokedexEntry: Natu has a highly developed jumping ability. The Pokemon flaps and leaps onto tree branches that are taller than grown-up people to pick at the tree's new shoots.

description:
Pokemon GO Xatu is a psychic flying type with 1975 MAX CP.
Xatu best moveset is Air Slash and Futuresight.
Xatu is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Xatu is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Xatu
