pokedexEntry: Xatu is known to stand motionless while staring at the sun all day long. Some people revere it as a mystical Pokemon out of their belief that Xatu is in possession of the power to see into the future.

description:
Pokemon GO Mareep is a electric type with 887 MAX CP.
Mareep best moveset is Thunder Shock and Thunderbolt.
Mareep is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Mareep is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Mareep
pokedexEntry: Mareep's fluffy coat of wool rubs together and builds a static charge. The more static electricity is charged, the more brightly the lightbulb at the tip of its tail glows.

description:
Pokemon GO Flaaffy is a electric type with 1402 MAX CP.
Flaaffy best moveset is Charge Beam and Thunderbolt.
Flaaffy is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Flaaffy is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Flaaffy
pokedexEntry: Flaaffy's wool quality changes so that it can generate a high amount of static electricity with a small amount of wool. The bare and slick parts of its hide are shielded against electricity.

description:
Pokemon GO Ampharos is a electric type with 2695 MAX CP.
Ampharos best moveset is Charge Beam and Zap Cannon.
Ampharos is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Ampharos is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Ampharos
pokedexEntry: Ampharos gives off so much light that it can be seen even from space. People in the old days used the light of this Pokemon to send signals back and forth with others far away.

description:
Pokemon GO Bellossom is a grass type with 2108 MAX CP.
Bellossom best moveset is Razor Leaf and Leaf Blade.
Bellossom is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Bellossom is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Bellossom
pokedexEntry: A Bellossom grows flowers more beautifully if it has evolved from a smelly Gloom—the more stinky the better. At night, this Pokemon closes its petals and goes to sleep.

description:
Pokemon GO Marill is a water fairy type with 420 MAX CP.
Marill best moveset is Bubble and Aqua Tail.
Marill is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Poison type moves.
Marill is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Marill
pokedexEntry: When fishing for food at the edge of a fast-running stream, Marill wraps its tail around the trunk of a tree. This Pokemon's tail is flexible and configured to stretch.

description:
Pokemon GO Azumarill is a water fairy type with 1503 MAX CP.
Azumarill best moveset is Bubble and Hydro Pump.
Azumarill is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Poison type moves.
Azumarill is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
name: Azumarill
pokedexEntry: Azumarill can make balloons out of air. It makes these air balloons if it spots a drowning Pokemon. The air balloons enable the Pokemon in trouble to breathe.

description:
Pokemon GO Sudowoodo is a rock type with 2065 MAX CP.
Sudowoodo best moveset is Rock Throw and Stone Edge.
Sudowoodo is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Steel, Water type moves.
Sudowoodo is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Sudowoodo
pokedexEntry: Sudowoodo camouflages itself as a tree to avoid being attacked by enemies. However, because its hands remain green throughout the year, the Pokemon is easily identified as a fake during the winter.

description:
Pokemon GO Politoed is a water type with 2371 MAX CP.
Politoed best moveset is Bubble and Hydro Pump.
Politoed is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Politoed is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Politoed
pokedexEntry: The curled hair on Politoed's head is proof of its status as a king. It is said that the longer and more curled the hair, the more respect this Pokemon earns from its peers.

description:
Pokemon GO Hoppip is a grass flying type with 508 MAX CP.
Hoppip best moveset is Bullet Seed and Grass Knot.
Hoppip is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice, Rock type moves.
Hoppip is boosted by Clear and Wind weather.
name: Hoppip
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon drifts and floats with the wind. If it senses the approach of strong winds, Hoppip links its leaves with other Hoppip to prepare against being blown away.

description:
Pokemon GO Skiploom is a grass flying type with 882 MAX CP.
Skiploom best moveset is Tackle and Grass Knot.
Skiploom is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice, Rock type moves.
Skiploom is boosted by Clear and Wind weather.
name: Skiploom
pokedexEntry: Skiploom's flower blossoms when the temperature rises above 64 degrees Fahrenheit. How much the flower opens depends on the temperature. For that reason, this Pokemon is sometimes used as a thermometer.

description:
Pokemon GO Jumpluff is a grass flying type with 1553 MAX CP.
Jumpluff best moveset is Infestation and Solar Beam.
Jumpluff is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice, Rock type moves.
Jumpluff is boosted by Clear and Wind weather.
name: Jumpluff
pokedexEntry: Jumpluff rides warm southern winds to cross the sea and fly to foreign lands. The Pokemon descends to the ground when it encounters cold air while it is floating.

description:
Pokemon GO Aipom is a normal type with 1188 MAX CP.
Aipom best moveset is Scratch and Swift.
Aipom is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Aipom is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Aipom
pokedexEntry: Aipom's tail ends in a hand-like appendage that can be cleverly manipulated. However, because the Pokemon uses its tail so much, its real hands have become rather clumsy.

description:
Pokemon GO Sunkern is a grass type with 316 MAX CP.
Sunkern best moveset is Cut and Grass Knot.
Sunkern is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Sunkern is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Sunkern
pokedexEntry: Sunkern tries to move as little as it possibly can. It does so because it tries to conserve all the nutrients it has stored in its body for its evolution. It will not eat a thing, subsisting only on morning dew.

description:
Pokemon GO Sunflora is a grass type with 2048 MAX CP.
Sunflora best moveset is Bullet Seed and Solar Beam.
Sunflora is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Sunflora is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Sunflora
pokedexEntry: Sunflora converts solar energy into nutrition. It moves around actively in the daytime when it is warm. It stops moving as soon as the sun goes down for the night.

description:
Pokemon GO Yanma is a bug flying type with 1326 MAX CP.
Yanma best moveset is Quick Attack and Aerial Ace.
Yanma is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Yanma is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Yanma
pokedexEntry: Yanma is capable of seeing 360 degrees without having to move its eyes. It is a great flier that is adept at making sudden stops and turning midair. This Pokemon uses its flying ability to quickly chase down targeted prey.

description:
Pokemon GO Wooper is a water ground type with 596 MAX CP.
Wooper best moveset is Water Gun and Mud Bomb.
Wooper is vulnerable to Grass type moves.
Wooper is boosted by Rain and Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Wooper
pokedexEntry: Wooper usually lives in water. However, it occasionally comes out onto land in search of food. On land, it coats its body with a gooey, toxic film.

description:
Pokemon GO Quagsire is a water ground type with 1929 MAX CP.
Quagsire best moveset is Mud Shot and Earthquake.
Quagsire is vulnerable to Grass type moves.
Quagsire is boosted by Rain and Clear weather.
name: Quagsire
pokedexEntry: Quagsire hunts for food by leaving its mouth wide open in water and waiting for its prey to blunder in unaware. Because the Pokemon does not move, it does not get very hungry.

description:
Pokemon GO Espeon is a psychic type with 3000 MAX CP.
Espeon best moveset is Confusion and Futuresight.
Espeon is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Espeon is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Espeon
pokedexEntry: Espeon is extremely loyal to any Trainer it considers to be worthy. It is said that this Pokemon developed its precognitive powers to protect its Trainer from harm.

description:
Pokemon GO Umbreon is a dark type with 2052 MAX CP.
Umbreon best moveset is Snarl and Foul Play.
Umbreon is vulnerable to Bug, Fairy, Fighting type moves.
Umbreon is boosted by Fog weather.
name: Umbreon
pokedexEntry: Umbreon evolved as a result of exposure to the moon's waves. It hides silently in darkness and waits for its foes to make a move. The rings on its body glow when it leaps to attack.

description:
Pokemon GO Murkrow is a dark flying type with 1392 MAX CP.
Murkrow best moveset is Feint Attack and Drill Peck.
Murkrow is vulnerable to Fairy, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Murkrow is boosted by Fog and Wind weather.
name: Murkrow
pokedexEntry: Murkrow was feared and loathed as the alleged bearer of ill fortune. This Pokemon shows strong interest in anything that sparkles or glitters. It will even try to steal rings from women.

description:
Pokemon GO Slowking is a water psychic type with 2482 MAX CP.
Slowking best moveset is Confusion and Psychic.
Slowking is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Slowking is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Slowking
pokedexEntry: Slowking undertakes research every day in an effort to solve the mysteries of the world. However, this Pokemon apparently forgets everything it has learned if the Shellder on its head comes off.

description:
Pokemon GO Misdreavus is a ghost type with 1781 MAX CP.
Misdreavus best moveset is Hex and Ominous Wind.
Misdreavus is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost type moves.
Misdreavus is boosted by Fog weather.
name: Misdreavus
pokedexEntry: Misdreavus frightens people with a creepy, sobbing cry. The Pokemon apparently uses its red spheres to absorb the fearful feelings of foes and turn them into nutrition.

description:
Pokemon GO Unown is a psychic type with 1022 MAX CP.
Unown best moveset is Hidden Power and Struggle.
Unown is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Unown is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Unown
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon is shaped like ancient writing. It is a mystery as to which came first, the ancient writings or the various Unown. Research into this topic is ongoing but nothing is known.

description:
Pokemon GO Wobbuffet is a psychic type with 1024 MAX CP.
Wobbuffet best moveset is Counter and Mirror Coat.
Wobbuffet is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Wobbuffet is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Wobbuffet
pokedexEntry: Wobbuffet does nothing but endure attacks—it won't attack on its own. However, it won't endure an attack on its tail. When that happens, the Pokemon will try to take the foe with it using Destiny Bond.

description:
Pokemon GO Girafarig is a normal psychic type with 1863 MAX CP.
Girafarig best moveset is Confusion and Psychic.
Girafarig is vulnerable to Bug, Dark type moves.
Girafarig is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
name: Girafarig
pokedexEntry: Girafarig's rear head contains a tiny brain that is too small for thinking. However, the rear head doesn't need to sleep, so it can keep watch over its surroundings 24 hours a day.

description:
Pokemon GO Pineco is a bug type with 1045 MAX CP.
Pineco best moveset is Bug Bite and Gyro Ball.
Pineco is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock type moves.
Pineco is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Pineco
pokedexEntry: Pineco hangs from a tree branch and patiently waits for prey to come along. If the Pokemon is disturbed while eating by someone shaking its tree, it drops down to the ground and explodes with no warning.

description:
Pokemon GO Forretress is a bug steel type with 2263 MAX CP.
Forretress best moveset is Bug Bite and Heavy Slam.
Forretress is vulnerable to Fire type moves.
Forretress is boosted by Rain and Snow weather.
name: Forretress
pokedexEntry: Forretress conceals itself inside its hardened steel shell. The shell is opened when the Pokemon is catching prey, but it does so at such a quick pace that the shell's inside cannot be seen.

description:
Pokemon GO Dunsparce is a normal type with 1615 MAX CP.
Dunsparce best moveset is Astonish and Drill Run.
Dunsparce is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Dunsparce is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Dunsparce
pokedexEntry: Dunsparce has a drill for its tail. It uses this tail to burrow into the ground backward. This Pokemon is known to make its nest in complex shapes deep under the ground.

description:
Pokemon GO Gligar is a ground flying type with 1758 MAX CP.
Gligar best moveset is Wing Attack and Dig.
Gligar is vulnerable to Ice, Water type moves.
Gligar is boosted by Clear and Wind weather.
name: Gligar
pokedexEntry: Gligar glides through the air without a sound as if it were sliding. This Pokemon hangs on to the face of its foe using its clawed hind legs and the large pincers on its forelegs, then injects the prey with its poison barb.

description:
Pokemon GO Steelix is a steel ground type with 2439 MAX CP.
Steelix best moveset is Iron Tail and Heavy Slam.
Steelix is vulnerable to Fighting, Ground, Fire, Water type moves.
Steelix is boosted by Snow and Clear weather.
name: Steelix
pokedexEntry: Steelix lives even further underground than Onix. This Pokemon is known to dig toward the earth's core. There are records of this Pokemon reaching a depth of over six-tenths of a mile underground.

description:
Pokemon GO Snubbull is a fairy type with 1124 MAX CP.
Snubbull best moveset is Bite and Dazzling Gleam.
Snubbull is vulnerable to Poison, Steel type moves.
Snubbull is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Snubbull
pokedexEntry: By baring its fangs and making a scary face, Snubbull sends smaller Pokemon scurrying away in terror. However, this Pokemon seems a little sad at making its foes flee.

description:
Pokemon GO Granbull is a fairy type with 2440 MAX CP.
Granbull best moveset is Snarl and Play Rough.
Granbull is vulnerable to Poison, Steel type moves.
Granbull is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Granbull
pokedexEntry: Granbull has a particularly well-developed lower jaw. The enormous fangs are heavy, causing the Pokemon to tip its head back for balance. Unless it is startled, it will not try to bite indiscriminately.

description:
Pokemon GO Qwilfish is a water poison type with 1910 MAX CP.
Qwilfish best moveset is Water Gun and Aqua Tail.
Qwilfish is vulnerable to Electric, Ground, Psychic type moves.
Qwilfish is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
name: Qwilfish
pokedexEntry: Qwilfish sucks in water, inflating itself. This Pokemon uses the pressure of the water it swallowed to shoot toxic quills all at once from all over its body. It finds swimming somewhat challenging.

description:
Pokemon GO Scizor is a bug steel type with 2801 MAX CP.
Scizor best moveset is Fury Cutter and X Scissor.
Scizor is vulnerable to Fire type moves.
Scizor is boosted by Rain and Snow weather.
name: Scizor
pokedexEntry: Scizor has a body with the hardness of steel. It is not easily fazed by ordinary sorts of attacks. This Pokemon flaps its wings to regulate its body temperature.

description:
Pokemon GO Shuckle is a bug rock type with 300 MAX CP.
Shuckle best moveset is Rock Throw and Stone Edge.
Shuckle is vulnerable to Rock, Steel, Water type moves.
Shuckle is boosted by Rain and PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Shuckle
pokedexEntry: Shuckle quietly hides itself under rocks, keeping its body concealed inside its hard shell while eating berries it has stored away. The berries mix with its body fluids to become a juice.

description:
Pokemon GO Heracross is a bug fighting type with 2938 MAX CP.
Heracross best moveset is Counter and Close Combat.
Heracross is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Fairy, Psychic type moves.
Heracross is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
name: Heracross
pokedexEntry: Heracross has sharp claws on its feet. These are planted firmly into the ground or the bark of a tree, giving the Pokemon a secure and solid footing to forcefully fling away foes with its proud horn.

description:
Pokemon GO Sneasel is a dark ice type with 1868 MAX CP.
Sneasel best moveset is Feint Attack and Avalanche.
Sneasel is vulnerable to Bug, Fairy, Fighting, Rock, Steel, Fire type moves.
Sneasel is boosted by Fog and Snow
name: Sneasel
pokedexEntry: Sneasel scales trees by punching its hooked claws into the bark. This Pokemon seeks out unguarded nests and steals eggs for food while the parents are away.

description:
Pokemon GO Teddiursa is a normal type with 1184 MAX CP.
Teddiursa best moveset is Scratch and Play Rough.
Teddiursa is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Teddiursa is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Teddiursa
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon likes to lick its palms that are sweetened by being soaked in honey. Teddiursa concocts its own honey by blending fruits and pollen collected by Beedrill.

description:
Pokemon GO Ursaring is a normal type with 2760 MAX CP.
Ursaring best moveset is Counter and Hyper Beam.
Ursaring is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Ursaring is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Ursaring
pokedexEntry: In the forests inhabited by Ursaring, it is said that there are many streams and towering trees where they gather food. This Pokemon walks through its forest gathering food every day.

description:
Pokemon GO Slugma is a fire type with 750 MAX CP.
Slugma best moveset is Ember and Flame Burst.
Slugma is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Slugma is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Slugma
pokedexEntry: Slugma does not have any blood in its body. Instead, intensely hot magma circulates throughout this Pokemon's body, carrying essential nutrients and oxygen to its organs.

description:
Pokemon GO Magcargo is a fire rock type with 1543 MAX CP.
Magcargo best moveset is Rock Throw and Overheat.
Magcargo is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water, Fighting type moves.
Magcargo is boosted by Clear and PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Magcargo
pokedexEntry: Magcargo's body temperature is approximately 18,000 degrees Fahrenheit. Water is vaporized on contact. If this Pokemon is caught in the rain, the raindrops instantly turn into steam, cloaking the area in a thick fog.

description:
Pokemon GO Swinub is a ice ground type with 663 MAX CP.
Swinub best moveset is Tackle and Rock Slide.
Swinub is vulnerable to Fighting, Steel, Fire, Grass, Water type moves.
Swinub is boosted by Snow and Clear weather.
name: Swinub
pokedexEntry: Swinub roots for food by rubbing its snout against the ground. Its favorite food is a mushroom that grows under the cover of dead grass. This Pokemon occasionally roots out hot springs.

description:
Pokemon GO Piloswine is a ice ground type with 2284 MAX CP.
Piloswine best moveset is Ice Shard and Avalanche.
Piloswine is vulnerable to Fighting, Steel, Fire, Grass, Water type moves.
Piloswine is boosted by Snow and Clear weather.
name: Piloswine
pokedexEntry: Piloswine is covered by a thick coat of long hair that enables it to endure the freezing cold. This Pokemon uses its tusks to dig up food that has been buried under ice.

description:
Pokemon GO Corsola is a water rock type with 1214 MAX CP.
Corsola best moveset is Bubble and Power Gem.
Corsola is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Fighting, Ground type moves.
Corsola is boosted by Rain and PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Corsola
pokedexEntry: Clusters of Corsola congregate in warm seas where they serve as ideal hiding places for smaller Pokemon. When the water temperature falls, this Pokemon migrates to the southern seas.

description:
Pokemon GO Remoraid is a water type with 749 MAX CP.
Remoraid best moveset is Water Gun and Water Pulse.
Remoraid is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Remoraid is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Remoraid
pokedexEntry: Remoraid sucks in water, then expels it at high velocity using its abdominal muscles to shoot down flying prey. When evolution draws near, this Pokemon travels downstream from rivers.

description:
Pokemon GO Octillery is a water type with 2124 MAX CP.
Octillery best moveset is Water Gun and Gunk Shot.
Octillery is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Octillery is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Octillery
pokedexEntry: Octillery grabs onto its foe using its tentacles. This Pokemon tries to immobilize it before delivering the finishing blow. If the foe turns out to be too strong, Octillery spews ink to escape.

description:
Pokemon GO Delibird is a ice flying type with 937 MAX CP.
Delibird best moveset is Quick Attack and Ice Punch.
Delibird is vulnerable to Rock, Steel, Fire, Electric type moves.
Delibird is boosted by Snow and Wind weather.
name: Delibird
pokedexEntry: Delibird carries its food bundled up in its tail. There once was a famous explorer who managed to reach the peak of the world's highest mountain, thanks to one of these Pokemon sharing its food.

description:
Pokemon GO Mantine is a water flying type with 2032 MAX CP.
Mantine best moveset is Bubble and Aerial Ace.
Mantine is vulnerable to Electric, Rock type moves.
Mantine is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Mantine
pokedexEntry: On sunny days, schools of Mantine can be seen elegantly leaping over the sea's waves. This Pokemon is not bothered by the Remoraid that hitches rides.

description:
Pokemon GO Skarmory is a steel flying type with 2032 MAX CP.
Skarmory best moveset is Steel Wing and Sky Attack.
Skarmory is vulnerable to Fire, Electric type moves.
Skarmory is boosted by Snow and Wind weather.
name: Skarmory
pokedexEntry: Skarmory's steel wings become tattered and bashed in from repeated battles. Once a year, the battered wings grow back completely, restoring the cutting edges to their pristine state.

description:
Pokemon GO Houndour is a dark fire type with 1110 MAX CP.
Houndour best moveset is Feint Attack and Flamethrower.
Houndour is vulnerable to Fighting, Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Houndour is boosted by Fog and Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Houndour
pokedexEntry: Houndour hunt as a coordinated pack. They communicate with each other using a variety of cries to corner their prey. This Pokemon's remarkable teamwork is unparalleled.

description:
Pokemon GO Houndoom is a dark fire type with 2529 MAX CP.
Houndoom best moveset is Fire Fang and Foul Play.
Houndoom is vulnerable to Fighting, Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Houndoom is boosted by Fog and Clear weather.
name: Houndoom
pokedexEntry: In a Houndoom pack, the one with its horns raked sharply toward the back serves a leadership role. These Pokemon choose their leader by fighting among themselves.

description:
Pokemon GO Kingdra is a water dragon type with 2424 MAX CP.
Kingdra best moveset is Water Gun and Outrage.
Kingdra is vulnerable to Dragon, Fairy type moves.
Kingdra is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Kingdra
pokedexEntry: Kingdra sleeps on the seafloor where it is otherwise devoid of life. When a storm arrives, the Pokemon is said to awaken and wander about in search of prey.

description:
Pokemon GO Phanpy is a ground type with 1175 MAX CP.
Phanpy best moveset is Tackle and Bulldoze.
Phanpy is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water type moves.
Phanpy is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Phanpy
pokedexEntry: Phanpy uses its long nose to shower itself. When others gather around, they thoroughly douse each other with water. These Pokemon can be seen drying their soaking-wet bodies at the edge of water.

description:
Pokemon GO Donphan is a ground type with 3022 MAX CP.
Donphan best moveset is Counter and Earthquake.
Donphan is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water type moves.
Donphan is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Donphan
pokedexEntry: If Donphan were to tackle with its hard body, even a house could be destroyed. Using its massive strength, the Pokemon helps clear rock and mud slides that block mountain trails.

description:
Pokemon GO Porygon2 is a normal type with 2546 MAX CP.
Porygon2 best moveset is Hidden Power and Hyper Beam.
Porygon2 is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Porygon2 is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Porygon2
pokedexEntry: Porygon2 was created by humans using the power of science. The man-made Pokemon has been endowed with artificial intelligence that enables it to learn new gestures and emotions on its own.

description:
Pokemon GO Stantler is a normal type with 1988 MAX CP.
Stantler best moveset is Tackle and Stomp.
Stantler is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Stantler is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Stantler
pokedexEntry: Stantler's magnificent antlers were traded at high prices as works of art. As a result, this Pokemon was hunted close to extinction by those who were after the priceless antlers.

description:
Pokemon GO Smeargle is a normal type with 389 MAX CP.
Smeargle best moveset is Tackle and Struggle.
Smeargle is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Smeargle is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Smeargle
pokedexEntry: Smeargle marks the boundaries of its territory using a body fluid that leaks out from the tip of its tail. Over 5,000 different marks left by this Pokemon have been found.

description:
Pokemon GO Tyrogue is a fighting type with 404 MAX CP.
Tyrogue best moveset is Rock Smash and Brick Break.
Tyrogue is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Tyrogue is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Tyrogue
pokedexEntry: Tyrogue becomes stressed out if it does not get to train every day. When raising this Pokemon, the Trainer must establish and uphold various training methods.

description:
Pokemon GO Hitmontop is a fighting type with 1905 MAX CP.
Hitmontop best moveset is Counter and Close Combat.
Hitmontop is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Hitmontop is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Hitmontop
pokedexEntry: Hitmontop spins on its head at high speed, all the while delivering kicks. This technique is a remarkable mix of both offense and defense at the same time. The Pokemon travels faster spinning than it does walking.

description:
Pokemon GO Smoochum is a ice psychic type with 1230 MAX CP.
Smoochum best moveset is Frost Breath and Ice Beam.
Smoochum is vulnerable to Rock, Steel, Fire, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Smoochum is boosted by Snow and Wind
name: Smoochum
pokedexEntry: Smoochum actively runs about, but also falls quite often. Whenever the chance arrives, it will look for its reflection to make sure its face hasn't become dirty.

description:
Pokemon GO Elekid is a electric type with 1073 MAX CP.
Elekid best moveset is Thunder Shock and Discharge.
Elekid is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Elekid is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Elekid
pokedexEntry: Elekid stores electricity in its body. If it touches metal and accidentally discharges all its built-up electricity, this Pokemon begins swinging its arms in circles to recharge itself.

description:
Pokemon GO Magby is a fire type with 1178 MAX CP.
Magby best moveset is Karate Chop and Flamethrower.
Magby is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Magby is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Magby
pokedexEntry: Magby's state of health is determined by observing the fire it breathes. If the Pokemon is spouting yellow flames from its mouth, it is in good health. When it is fatigued, black smoke will be mixed in with the flames.

description:
Pokemon GO Miltank is a normal type with 2312 MAX CP.
Miltank best moveset is Tackle and Body Slam.
Miltank is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Miltank is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Miltank
pokedexEntry: Miltank gives over five gallons of milk on a daily basis. Its sweet milk is enjoyed by children and grown-ups alike. People who can't drink milk turn it into yogurt and eat it instead.

description:
Pokemon GO Blissey is a normal type with 3219 MAX CP.
Blissey best moveset is Pound and Hyper Beam.
Blissey is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Blissey is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Blissey
pokedexEntry: Blissey senses sadness with its fluffy coat of fur. If it does so, this Pokemon will rush over to a sad person, no matter how far away, to share a Lucky Egg that brings a smile to any face.

description:
Pokemon GO Raikou is a electric type with 3349 MAX CP.
Raikou best moveset is Thunder Shock and Wild Charge.
Raikou is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Raikou is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Raikou
pokedexEntry: Raikou embodies the speed of lightning. The roars of this Pokemon send shock waves shuddering through the air and shake the ground as if lightning bolts had come crashing down.

description:
Pokemon GO Entei is a fire type with 3377 MAX CP.
Entei best moveset is Fire Fang and Overheat.
Entei is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Entei is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Entei
pokedexEntry: Entei embodies the passion of magma. This Pokemon is thought to have been born in the eruption of a volcano. It sends up massive bursts of fire that utterly consume all that they touch.

description:
Pokemon GO Suicune is a water type with 2823 MAX CP.
Suicune best moveset is Extrasensory and Hydro Pump.
Suicune is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Suicune is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Suicune
pokedexEntry: Suicune embodies the compassion of a pure spring of water. It runs across the land with gracefulness. This Pokemon has the power to purify dirty water.

description:
Pokemon GO Larvitar is a rock ground type with 904 MAX CP.
Larvitar best moveset is Bite and Ancient Power.
Larvitar is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Steel, Water, Ice type moves.
Larvitar is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Clear
name: Larvitar
pokedexEntry: Larvitar is born deep under the ground. To come up to the surface, this Pokemon must eat its way through the soil above. Until it does so, Larvitar cannot see its parents.

description:
Pokemon GO Pupitar is a rock ground type with 1608 MAX CP.
Pupitar best moveset is Bite and Ancient Power.
Pupitar is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Steel, Water, Ice type moves.
Pupitar is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Clear
name: Pupitar
pokedexEntry: Pupitar creates a gas inside its body that it compresses and forcefully ejects to propel itself like a jet. The body is very durable—it avoids damage even if it hits solid steel.

description:
Pokemon GO Tyranitar is a rock dark type with 3670 MAX CP.
Tyranitar best moveset is Bite and Stone Edge.
Tyranitar is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Steel, Water, Bug, Fairy type moves.
Tyranitar is boosted by
name: Tyranitar
pokedexEntry: Tyranitar is so overwhelmingly powerful, it can bring down a whole mountain to make its nest. This Pokemon wanders about in mountains seeking new opponents to fight.

description:
Pokemon GO Lugia is a psychic flying type with 3598 MAX CP.
Lugia best moveset is Extrasensory and Futuresight.
Lugia is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Lugia is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Lugia
pokedexEntry: Lugia's wings pack devastating power—a light fluttering of its wings can blow apart regular houses. As a result, this Pokemon chooses to live out of sight deep under the sea.

description:
Pokemon GO Ho-oh is a fire flying type with 3889 MAX CP.
Ho-oh best moveset is Steel Wing and Brave Bird.
Ho-oh is vulnerable to Rock, Water, Electric type moves.
Ho-oh is boosted by Clear and Wind weather.
name: Ho-oh
pokedexEntry: Ho-Oh's feathers glow in seven colors depending on the angle at which they are struck by light. These feathers are said to bring happiness to the bearers. This Pokemon is said to live at the foot of a rainbow.

description:
Pokemon GO Celebi is a psychic grass type with 3090 MAX CP.
Celebi best moveset is Confusion and Psychic.
Celebi is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Celebi is boosted by
name: Celebi
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon came from the future by crossing over time. It is thought that so long as Celebi appears, a bright and shining future awaits us.

description:
Pokemon GO Treecko is a grass type with 923 MAX CP.
Treecko best moveset is Pound and Grass Knot.
Treecko is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Treecko is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Treecko
pokedexEntry: Treecko is cool, calm, and collected—it never panics under any situation. If a bigger foe were to glare at this Pokemon, it would glare right back without conceding an inch of ground.

description:
Pokemon GO Grovyle is a grass type with 1508 MAX CP.
Grovyle best moveset is Quick Attack and Grass Knot.
Grovyle is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Grovyle is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Grovyle
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon adeptly flies from branch to branch in trees. In a forest, no Pokemon can ever hope to catch a fleeing Grovyle however fast they may be.

description:
Pokemon GO Sceptile is a grass type with 2584 MAX CP.
Sceptile best moveset is Fury Cutter and Leaf Blade.
Sceptile is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Sceptile is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Sceptile
pokedexEntry: Sceptile has seeds growing on its back. They are said to be bursting with nutrients that revitalize trees. This Pokemon raises the trees in a forest with loving care.

description:
Pokemon GO Torchic is a fire type with 959 MAX CP.
Torchic best moveset is Ember and Flamethrower.
Torchic is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Torchic is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Torchic
pokedexEntry: Torchic has a place inside its body where it keeps its flame. Give it a hug—it will be glowing with warmth. This Pokemon is covered all over by a fluffy coat of down.

description:
Pokemon GO Combusken is a fire fighting type with 1472 MAX CP.
Combusken best moveset is Ember and Flamethrower.
Combusken is vulnerable to Ground, Water, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Combusken is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Combusken
pokedexEntry: Combusken battles with the intensely hot flames it spews from its beak and with outstandingly destructive kicks. This Pokemon's cry is very loud and distracting.

description:
Pokemon GO Blaziken is a fire fighting type with 2631 MAX CP.
Blaziken best moveset is Counter and Overheat.
Blaziken is vulnerable to Ground, Water, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Blaziken is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
name: Blaziken
pokedexEntry: Blaziken has incredibly strong legs—it can easily clear a 30-story building in one leap. This Pokemon's blazing punches leave its foes scorched and blackened.

description:
Pokemon GO Mudkip is a water type with 981 MAX CP.
Mudkip best moveset is Tackle and Stomp.
Mudkip is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Mudkip is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Mudkip
pokedexEntry: In water, Mudkip breathes using the gills on its cheeks. If it is faced with a tight situation in battle, this Pokemon will unleash its amazing power—it can crush rocks bigger than itself.

description:
Pokemon GO Marshtomp is a water ground type with 1617 MAX CP.
Marshtomp best moveset is Water Gun and Surf.
Marshtomp is vulnerable to Grass type moves.
Marshtomp is boosted by Rain and Clear weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Marshtomp
pokedexEntry: Marshtomp is much faster at traveling through mud than it is at swimming. This Pokemon's hindquarters exhibit obvious development, giving it the ability to walk on just its hind legs.

description:
Pokemon GO Swampert is a water ground type with 2815 MAX CP.
Swampert best moveset is Water Gun and Surf.
Swampert is vulnerable to Grass type moves.
Swampert is boosted by Rain and Clear weather.
name: Swampert
pokedexEntry: Swampert predicts storms by sensing subtle differences in the sounds of waves and tidal winds with its fins. If a storm is approaching, it piles up boulders to protect itself.

description:
Pokemon GO Poochyena is a dark type with 564 MAX CP.
Poochyena best moveset is Snarl and Crunch.
Poochyena is vulnerable to Bug, Fairy, Fighting type moves.
Poochyena is boosted by Fog weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Poochyena
pokedexEntry: Poochyena is an omnivore—it will eat anything. A distinguishing feature is how large its fangs are compared to its body. This Pokemon tries to intimidate its foes by making the hair on its tail bristle out.

description:
Pokemon GO Mightyena is a dark type with 1783 MAX CP.
Mightyena best moveset is Bite and Crunch.
Mightyena is vulnerable to Bug, Fairy, Fighting type moves.
Mightyena is boosted by Fog weather.
name: Mightyena
pokedexEntry: Mightyena travel and act as a pack in the wild. The memory of its life in the wild compels the Pokemon to obey only those Trainers that it recognizes to possess superior skill.

description:
Pokemon GO Zigzagoon is a normal type with 423 MAX CP.
Zigzagoon best moveset is Tackle and Grass Knot.
Zigzagoon is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Zigzagoon is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Zigzagoon
pokedexEntry: The hair on Zigzagoon's back is bristly. It rubs the hard back hair against trees to leave its territorial markings. This Pokemon may play dead to fool foes in battle.

description:
Pokemon GO Linoone is a normal type with 1533 MAX CP.
Linoone best moveset is Tackle and Grass Knot.
Linoone is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Linoone is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Linoone
pokedexEntry: When hunting, Linoone will make a beeline straight for the prey at a full run. While this Pokemon is capable of topping 60 mph, it has to come to a screeching halt before it can turn.

description:
Pokemon GO Wurmple is a bug type with 502 MAX CP.
Wurmple best moveset is Bug Bite and Struggle.
Wurmple is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock type moves.
Wurmple is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 12 candy to evolve!
name: Wurmple
pokedexEntry: Wurmple is targeted by Swellow as prey. This Pokemon will try to resist by pointing the spikes on its rear at the attacking predator. It will weaken the foe by leaking poison from the spikes.

description:
Pokemon GO Silcoon is a bug type with 517 MAX CP.
Silcoon best moveset is Bug Bite and Struggle.
Silcoon is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock type moves.
Silcoon is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Silcoon
pokedexEntry: Silcoon was thought to endure hunger and not consume anything before its evolution. However, it is now thought that this Pokemon slakes its thirst by drinking rainwater that collects on its silk.

description:
Pokemon GO Beautifly is a bug flying type with 1573 MAX CP.
Beautifly best moveset is Infestation and Bug Buzz.
Beautifly is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Beautifly is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Beautifly
pokedexEntry: Beautifly has a long mouth like a coiled needle, which is very convenient for collecting pollen from flowers. This Pokemon rides the spring winds as it flits around gathering pollen.

description:
Pokemon GO Cascoon is a bug type with 517 MAX CP.
Cascoon best moveset is Bug Bite and Struggle.
Cascoon is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock type moves.
Cascoon is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Cascoon
pokedexEntry: If it is attacked, Cascoon remains motionless however badly it may be hurt. It does so because if it were to move, its body would be weak upon evolution. This Pokemon will also not forget the pain it endured.

description:
Pokemon GO Dustox is a bug poison type with 1121 MAX CP.
Dustox best moveset is Struggle Bug and Sludge Bomb.
Dustox is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Psychic type moves.
Dustox is boosted by Rain and Cloudy weather.
name: Dustox
pokedexEntry: When Dustox flaps its wings, a fine dust is scattered all over. This dust is actually a powerful poison that will even make a pro wrestler sick. This Pokemon searches for food using its antennae like radar.

description:
Pokemon GO Lotad is a water grass type with 526 MAX CP.
Lotad best moveset is Water Gun and Energy Ball.
Lotad is vulnerable to Bug, Flying, Poison type moves.
Lotad is boosted by Rain and Clear weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Lotad
pokedexEntry: Lotad is said to have dwelled on land before. However, this Pokemon is thought to have returned to water because the leaf on its head grew large and heavy. It now lives by floating atop the water.

description:
Pokemon GO Lombre is a water grass type with 1102 MAX CP.
Lombre best moveset is Razor Leaf and Grass Knot.
Lombre is vulnerable to Bug, Flying, Poison type moves.
Lombre is boosted by Rain and Clear weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Lombre
pokedexEntry: Lombre's entire body is covered by a slippery, slimy film. It feels horribly unpleasant to be touched by this Pokemon's hands. Lombre is often mistaken for a human child.

description:
Pokemon GO Ludicolo is a water grass type with 2229 MAX CP.
Ludicolo best moveset is Razor Leaf and Solar Beam.
Ludicolo is vulnerable to Bug, Flying, Poison type moves.
Ludicolo is boosted by Rain and Clear weather.
name: Ludicolo
pokedexEntry: Upon hearing an upbeat and cheerful rhythm, the cells in Ludicolo's body become very energetic and active. Even in battle, this Pokemon will exhibit an amazing amount of power.

description:
Pokemon GO Seedot is a grass type with 526 MAX CP.
Seedot best moveset is Quick Attack and Grass Knot.
Seedot is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Seedot is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Seedot
pokedexEntry: Seedot looks exactly like an acorn when it is dangling from a tree branch. It startles other Pokemon by suddenly moving. This Pokemon polishes its body once a day using leaves.

description:
Pokemon GO Nuzleaf is a grass dark type with 1117 MAX CP.
Nuzleaf best moveset is Feint Attack and Grass Knot.
Nuzleaf is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice, Fairy, Fighting type moves.
Nuzleaf is boosted by
name: Nuzleaf
pokedexEntry: This Pokemon pulls out the leaf on its head and makes a flute with it. The sound of Nuzleaf's flute strikes fear and uncertainty in the hearts of people lost in a forest.

description:
Pokemon GO Shiftry is a grass dark type with 2186 MAX CP.
Shiftry best moveset is Feint Attack and Leaf Blade.
Shiftry is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice, Fairy, Fighting type moves.
Shiftry is boosted by
name: Shiftry
pokedexEntry: Shiftry's large fans generate awesome gusts of wind at a speed close to 100 feet per second. The whipped-up wind blows anything away. This Pokemon chooses to live quietly deep in forests.

description:
Pokemon GO Taillow is a normal flying type with 642 MAX CP.
Taillow best moveset is Quick Attack and Aerial Ace.
Taillow is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Taillow is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Taillow
pokedexEntry: Taillow is young—it has only just left its nest. As a result, it sometimes becomes lonesome and cries at night. This Pokemon feeds on Wurmple that live in forests.

description:
Pokemon GO Swellow is a normal flying type with 1747 MAX CP.
Swellow best moveset is Wing Attack and Sky Attack.
Swellow is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Swellow is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
name: Swellow
pokedexEntry: Swellow is very conscientious about the upkeep of its glossy wings. Once two Swellow are gathered, they diligently take care of cleaning each other's wings.

description:
Pokemon GO Wingull is a water flying type with 642 MAX CP.
Wingull best moveset is Water Gun and Air Cutter.
Wingull is vulnerable to Electric, Rock type moves.
Wingull is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Wingull
pokedexEntry: Wingull rides updrafts rising from the sea by extending its long and narrow wings to glide. This Pokemon's long beak is useful for catching prey.

description:
Pokemon GO Pelipper is a water flying type with 1969 MAX CP.
Pelipper best moveset is Wing Attack and Hydro Pump.
Pelipper is vulnerable to Electric, Rock type moves.
Pelipper is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Pelipper
pokedexEntry: Pelipper searches for food while in flight by skimming the wave tops. This Pokemon dips its large bill in the sea to scoop up food, then swallows everything in one big gulp.

description:
Pokemon GO Ralts is a psychic fairy type with 436 MAX CP.
Ralts best moveset is Confusion and Psyshock.
Ralts is vulnerable to Ghost, Poison, Steel type moves.
Ralts is boosted by Wind and Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Ralts
pokedexEntry: Ralts has the ability to sense the emotions of people. If its Trainer is in a cheerful mood, this Pokemon grows cheerful and joyous in the same way.

description:
Pokemon GO Kirlia is a psychic fairy type with 843 MAX CP.
Kirlia best moveset is Confusion and Psychic.
Kirlia is vulnerable to Ghost, Poison, Steel type moves.
Kirlia is boosted by Wind and Cloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Kirlia
pokedexEntry: Kirlia uses the horns on its head to amplify its psychokinetic power. When the Pokemon uses its power, the air around it becomes distorted, creating mirages of nonexistent scenery.

description:
Pokemon GO Gardevoir is a psychic fairy type with 2964 MAX CP.
Gardevoir best moveset is Confusion and Dazzling Gleam.
Gardevoir is vulnerable to Ghost, Poison, Steel type moves.
Gardevoir is boosted by Wind and Cloudy weather.
name: Gardevoir
pokedexEntry: Gardevoir has the psychokinetic power to distort the dimensions and create a small black hole. This Pokemon will try to protect its Trainer even at the risk of its own life.

description:
Pokemon GO Surskit is a bug water type with 695 MAX CP.
Surskit best moveset is Bubble and Signal Beam.
Surskit is vulnerable to Flying, Rock, Electric type moves.
Surskit is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Surskit
pokedexEntry: If Surskit senses danger, it secretes a thick, sugary syrup from the tip of its head. There are some Pokemon that love eating this syrup.

description:
Pokemon GO Masquerain is a bug flying type with 2135 MAX CP.
Masquerain best moveset is Infestation and Silver Wind.
Masquerain is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Masquerain is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Masquerain
pokedexEntry: Masquerain's antennas have eyelike patterns that usually give it an angry look. If the “eyes” are droopy and appear sad, it is said to be a sign that a heavy rainfall is on its way.

description:
Pokemon GO Shroomish is a grass type with 722 MAX CP.
Shroomish best moveset is Bullet Seed and Grass Knot.
Shroomish is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Shroomish is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Shroomish
pokedexEntry: If Shroomish senses danger, it shakes its body and scatters spores from the top of its head. This Pokemon's spores are so toxic, they make trees and weeds wilt.

description:
Pokemon GO Breloom is a grass fighting type with 2407 MAX CP.
Breloom best moveset is Counter and Dynamic Punch.
Breloom is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice, Fairy, Psychic type moves.
Breloom is boosted by Clear and Cloudy
name: Breloom
pokedexEntry: The seeds ringing Breloom's tail are made of hardened toxic spores. It is horrible to eat the seeds. Just taking a bite of this Pokemon's seed will cause your stomach to rumble.

description:
Pokemon GO Slakoth is a normal type with 942 MAX CP.
Slakoth best moveset is Yawn and Body Slam.
Slakoth is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Slakoth is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Slakoth
pokedexEntry: Slakoth's heart beats just once a minute. Whatever happens, it is content to loaf around motionless. It is rare to see this Pokemon in motion.

description:
Pokemon GO Vigoroth is a normal type with 1896 MAX CP.
Vigoroth best moveset is Scratch and Body Slam.
Vigoroth is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Vigoroth is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Vigoroth
pokedexEntry: Vigoroth is simply incapable of remaining still. Even when it tries to sleep, the blood in its veins grows agitated, compelling this Pokemon to run wild throughout the jungle before it can settle down.

description:
Pokemon GO Slaking is a normal type with 4548 MAX CP.
Slaking best moveset is Yawn and Hyper Beam.
Slaking is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Slaking is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Slaking
pokedexEntry: Wherever Slaking live, rings of over a yard in diameter appear in grassy fields. They are made by the Pokemon as it eats all the grass within reach while lying prone on the ground.

description:
Pokemon GO Nincada is a bug ground type with 674 MAX CP.
Nincada best moveset is Bug Bite and Bug Buzz.
Nincada is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Water type moves.
Nincada is boosted by Rain and Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Nincada
pokedexEntry: Nincada lives underground. It uses its sharp claws to carve the roots of trees and absorb moisture and nutrients. This Pokemon can't withstand bright sunlight so avoids it.

description:
Pokemon GO Ninjask is a bug flying type with 1751 MAX CP.
Ninjask best moveset is Fury Cutter and Bug Buzz.
Ninjask is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Ninjask is boosted by Rain and Wind weather.
name: Ninjask
pokedexEntry: If Ninjask is not trained properly, it will refuse to obey the Trainer and cry loudly continuously. Because of this quality, this Pokemon is said to be one that puts the Trainer's abilities to the test.

description:
Pokemon GO Shedinja is a bug ghost type with 421 MAX CP.
Shedinja best moveset is Struggle Bug and Shadow Sneak.
Shedinja is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Shedinja is boosted by Rain and Fog weather.
name: Shedinja
pokedexEntry: Shedinja is a peculiar Pokemon. It seems to appear unsought in a Poke Ball after a Nincada evolves. This bizarre Pokemon is entirely immobile—it doesn't even breathe.

description:
Pokemon GO Whismur is a normal type with 603 MAX CP.
Whismur best moveset is Pound and Stomp.
Whismur is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Whismur is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 12 candy to evolve!
name: Whismur
pokedexEntry: Whismur is very timid. If it starts to cry loudly, it becomes startled by its own crying and cries even harder. When it finally stops crying, the Pokemon goes to sleep, all tired out.

description:
Pokemon GO Loudred is a normal type with 1233 MAX CP.
Loudred best moveset is Bite and Stomp.
Loudred is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Loudred is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Loudred
pokedexEntry: Loudred shouts while stamping its feet. After it finishes shouting, this Pokemon becomes incapable of hearing anything for a while. This is considered to be a weak point.

description:
Pokemon GO Exploud is a normal type with 2267 MAX CP.
Exploud best moveset is Bite and Fire Blast.
Exploud is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Exploud is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Exploud
pokedexEntry: Exploud communicates its feelings to the others by emitting whistle-like sounds from the tubes on its body. This Pokemon only raises its voice when it is in battle.

description:
Pokemon GO Makuhita is a fighting type with 745 MAX CP.
Makuhita best moveset is Rock Smash and Cross Chop.
Makuhita is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Makuhita is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Makuhita
pokedexEntry: Makuhita has a tireless spirit—it will never give up hope. It eats a lot of food, gets plenty of sleep, and it trains very rigorously. By living that way, this Pokemon packs its body with energy.

description:
Pokemon GO Hariyama is a fighting type with 2765 MAX CP.
Hariyama best moveset is Counter and Dynamic Punch.
Hariyama is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Psychic type moves.
Hariyama is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Hariyama
pokedexEntry: Hariyama's thick body may appear fat, but it is actually a hunk of solid muscle. If this Pokemon bears down and tightens all its muscles, its body becomes as hard as a rock.

description:
Pokemon GO Azurill is a normal fairy type with 316 MAX CP.
Azurill best moveset is Bubble and Body Slam.
Azurill is vulnerable to Poison, Steel type moves.
Azurill is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Cloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Azurill
pokedexEntry: Azurill's tail is large and bouncy. It is packed full of the nutrients this Pokemon needs to grow. Azurill can be seen bouncing and playing on its big, rubbery tail.

description:
Pokemon GO Nosepass is a rock type with 831 MAX CP.
Nosepass best moveset is Rock Throw and Rock Slide.
Nosepass is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Steel, Water type moves.
Nosepass is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Nosepass
pokedexEntry: Nosepass had been said to be completely unmoving, with its magnetic nose pointed due north. However, close observation has revealed that the Pokemon actually moves by a little over 3/8 of an inch every year.

description:
Pokemon GO Skitty is a normal type with 659 MAX CP.
Skitty best moveset is Tackle and Wild Charge.
Skitty is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Skitty is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Skitty
pokedexEntry: Skitty is known to chase around playfully after its own tail. In the wild, this Pokemon lives in holes in the trees of forests. It is very popular as a pet because of its adorable looks.

description:
Pokemon GO Delcatty is a normal type with 1385 MAX CP.
Delcatty best moveset is Feint Attack and Wild Charge.
Delcatty is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Delcatty is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Delcatty
pokedexEntry: Delcatty sleeps anywhere it wants without keeping a permanent nest. If other Pokemon approach it as it sleeps, this Pokemon will never fight—it will just move away somewhere else.

description:
Pokemon GO Sableye is a dark ghost type with 1305 MAX CP.
Sableye best moveset is Shadow Claw and Foul Play.
Sableye is vulnerable to Fairy type moves.
Sableye is boosted by Fog weather.
name: Sableye
pokedexEntry: Sableye digs the ground with sharpened claws to find rocks that it eats. Substances in the eaten rocks crystallize and rise up to the Pokemon's body surface.

description:
Pokemon GO Mawile is a steel fairy type with 1484 MAX CP.
Mawile best moveset is Astonish and Play Rough.
Mawile is vulnerable to Ground, Fire type moves.
Mawile is boosted by Snow and Cloudy weather.
name: Mawile
pokedexEntry: Don't be taken in by this Pokemon's cute face—it's very dangerous. Mawile fools the foe into letting down its guard, then chomps down with its massive jaws. The steel jaws are really horns that have been transformed.

description:
Pokemon GO Aron is a steel rock type with 1232 MAX CP.
Aron best moveset is Metal Claw and Iron Head.
Aron is vulnerable to Fighting, Ground, Water type moves.
Aron is boosted by Snow and PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Aron
pokedexEntry: Aron has a body of steel. With one all-out charge, this Pokemon can demolish even a heavy dump truck. The destroyed dump truck then becomes a handy meal for the Pokemon.

description:
Pokemon GO Lairon is a steel rock type with 2004 MAX CP.
Lairon best moveset is Metal Claw and Rock Slide.
Lairon is vulnerable to Fighting, Ground, Water type moves.
Lairon is boosted by Snow and PartlyCloudy weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Lairon
pokedexEntry: Lairon feeds on iron contained in rocks and water. It makes its nest on mountains where iron ore is buried. As a result, the Pokemon often clashes with humans mining the iron ore.

description:
Pokemon GO Aggron is a steel rock type with 3004 MAX CP.
Aggron best moveset is Iron Tail and Heavy Slam.
Aggron is vulnerable to Fighting, Ground, Water type moves.
Aggron is boosted by Snow and PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Aggron
pokedexEntry: Aggron is protective of its environment. If its mountain is ravaged by a landslide or a fire, this Pokemon will haul topsoil to the area, plant trees, and beautifully restore its own territory.

description:
Pokemon GO Meditite is a fighting psychic type with 555 MAX CP.
Meditite best moveset is Confusion and Psyshock.
Meditite is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Ghost type moves.
Meditite is boosted by Cloudy and Wind weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Meditite
pokedexEntry: Meditite heightens its inner energy through meditation. It survives on just one berry a day. Minimal eating is another aspect of this Pokemon's training.

description:
Pokemon GO Medicham is a fighting psychic type with 1275 MAX CP.
Medicham best moveset is Counter and Dynamic Punch.
Medicham is vulnerable to Fairy, Flying, Ghost type moves.
Medicham is boosted by Cloudy and Wind weather.
name: Medicham
pokedexEntry: Through the power of meditation, Medicham developed its sixth sense. It gained the ability to use psychokinetic powers. This Pokemon is known to meditate for a whole month without eating.

description:
Pokemon GO Electrike is a electric type with 810 MAX CP.
Electrike best moveset is Spark and Discharge.
Electrike is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Electrike is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Electrike
pokedexEntry: Electrike runs faster than the human eye can follow. The friction from running is converted into electricity, which is then stored in this Pokemon's fur.

description:
Pokemon GO Manectric is a electric type with 2131 MAX CP.
Manectric best moveset is Charge Beam and Wild Charge.
Manectric is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Manectric is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Manectric
pokedexEntry: Manectric discharges strong electricity from its mane. The mane is used for collecting electricity in the atmosphere. This Pokemon creates thunderclouds above its head.

description:
Pokemon GO Plusle is a electric type with 1681 MAX CP.
Plusle best moveset is Spark and Thunderbolt.
Plusle is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Plusle is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Plusle
pokedexEntry: When Plusle is cheering on its partner, it flashes with electric sparks from all over its body. If its partner loses, this Pokemon cries loudly.

description:
Pokemon GO Minun is a electric type with 1585 MAX CP.
Minun best moveset is Spark and Discharge.
Minun is vulnerable to Ground type moves.
Minun is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Minun
pokedexEntry: Minun loves to cheer on its partner in battle. It gives off sparks from its body while it is doing so. If its partner is in trouble, this Pokemon gives off increasing amounts of sparks.

description:
Pokemon GO Volbeat is a bug type with 1620 MAX CP.
Volbeat best moveset is Struggle Bug and Bug Buzz.
Volbeat is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock type moves.
Volbeat is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Volbeat
pokedexEntry: Volbeat's tail glows like a lightbulb. With other Volbeat, it uses its tail to draw geometric shapes in the night sky. This Pokemon loves the sweet aroma given off by Illumise.

description:
Pokemon GO Illumise is a bug type with 1620 MAX CP.
Illumise best moveset is Struggle Bug and Bug Buzz.
Illumise is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Rock type moves.
Illumise is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Illumise
pokedexEntry: Illumise leads a flight of illuminated Volbeat to draw signs in the night sky. This Pokemon is said to earn greater respect from its peers by composing more complex designs in the sky.

description:
Pokemon GO Roselia is a grass poison type with 1718 MAX CP.
Roselia best moveset is Poison Jab and Sludge Bomb.
Roselia is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Ice, Psychic type moves.
Roselia is boosted by Clear and Cloudy weather.
name: Roselia
pokedexEntry: On extremely rare occasions, a Roselia is said to appear with its flowers in unusual colors. The thorns on this Pokemon's head contain a vicious poison.

description:
Pokemon GO Gulpin is a poison type with 788 MAX CP.
Gulpin best moveset is Pound and Gunk Shot.
Gulpin is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Gulpin is boosted by Cloudy weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Gulpin
pokedexEntry: Most of Gulpin's body is made up of its stomach—its heart and brain are very small in comparison. This Pokemon's stomach contains special enzymes that dissolve anything.

description:
Pokemon GO Swalot is a poison type with 1872 MAX CP.
Swalot best moveset is Infestation and Sludge Bomb.
Swalot is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Swalot is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Swalot
pokedexEntry: Swalot has no teeth, so what it eats, it swallows whole, no matter what. Its cavernous mouth yawns widely. An automobile tire could easily fit inside this Pokemon's mouth.

description:
Pokemon GO Carvanha is a water dark type with 874 MAX CP.
Carvanha best moveset is Snarl and Crunch.
Carvanha is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Bug, Fairy, Fighting type moves.
Carvanha is boosted by Rain and Fog weather.
name: Carvanha
pokedexEntry: If anything invades Carvanha's territory, it will swarm and tear at the intruder with its pointed fangs. On its own, however, this Pokemon turns suddenly timid.

description:
Pokemon GO Sharpedo is a water dark type with 1986 MAX CP.
Sharpedo best moveset is Bite and Hydro Pump.
Sharpedo is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Bug, Fairy, Fighting type moves.
Sharpedo is boosted by Rain and Fog weather.
name: Sharpedo
pokedexEntry: Sharpedo can swim at speeds of up to 75 mph by jetting seawater out of its backside. This Pokemon's drawback is its inability to swim long distances.

description:
Pokemon GO Wailmer is a water type with 1424 MAX CP.
Wailmer best moveset is Water Gun and Water Pulse.
Wailmer is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Wailmer is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 400 candy to evolve!
name: Wailmer
pokedexEntry: Wailmer can store water inside its body to transform itself into a ball for bouncing around on the ground. By filling itself up with more water, this Pokemon can elevate the height of its bounces.

description:
Pokemon GO Wailord is a water type with 2258 MAX CP.
Wailord best moveset is Water Gun and Surf.
Wailord is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Wailord is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Wailord
pokedexEntry: When chasing prey, Wailord herds them by leaping out of the water and making a humongous splash. It is breathtaking to see this Pokemon leaping out of the sea with others in its pod.

description:
Pokemon GO Numel is a fire ground type with 957 MAX CP.
Numel best moveset is Ember and Bulldoze.
Numel is vulnerable to Ground, Water type moves.
Numel is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Numel
pokedexEntry: Numel stores magma of almost 2,200 degrees Fahrenheit within its body. If it gets wet, the magma cools and hardens. In that event, the Pokemon's body grows heavy and its movements become sluggish.

description:
Pokemon GO Camerupt is a fire ground type with 2016 MAX CP.
Camerupt best moveset is Ember and Overheat.
Camerupt is vulnerable to Ground, Water type moves.
Camerupt is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Camerupt
pokedexEntry: The humps on Camerupt's back are formed by a transformation of its bones. They sometimes blast out molten magma. This Pokemon apparently erupts often when it is enraged.

description:
Pokemon GO Torkoal is a fire type with 2036 MAX CP.
Torkoal best moveset is Fire Spin and Overheat.
Torkoal is vulnerable to Rock, Ground, Water type moves.
Torkoal is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Torkoal
pokedexEntry: Torkoal generates energy by burning coal. It grows weaker as the fire dies down. When it is preparing for battle, this Pokemon burns more coal.

description:
Pokemon GO Spoink is a psychic type with 1285 MAX CP.
Spoink best moveset is Zen Headbutt and Shadow Ball.
Spoink is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Spoink is boosted by Wind weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Spoink
pokedexEntry: Spoink keeps a pearl on top of its head. The pearl functions to amplify this Pokemon's psychokinetic powers. It is therefore on a constant search for a bigger pearl.

description:
Pokemon GO Grumpig is a psychic type with 2310 MAX CP.
Grumpig best moveset is Extrasensory and Shadow Ball.
Grumpig is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Grumpig is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Grumpig
pokedexEntry: Grumpig uses the black pearls on its body to wield its fantastic powers. When it is doing so, it dances bizarrely. This Pokemon's black pearls are valuable as works of art.

description:
Pokemon GO Spinda is a normal type with 1088 MAX CP.
Spinda best moveset is Sucker Punch and Dig.
Spinda is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Spinda is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Spinda
pokedexEntry: No two Spinda are said to have identical spot patterns on their hides. This Pokemon moves in a curious manner as if it is stumbling in dizziness. Its lurching movements can cause the opponent to become confused.

description:
Pokemon GO Trapinch is a ground type with 1092 MAX CP.
Trapinch best moveset is Mud Shot and Dig.
Trapinch is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water type moves.
Trapinch is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Trapinch
pokedexEntry: Trapinch is a patient hunter. It digs an inescapable pit in a desert and waits for its prey to come tumbling down. This Pokemon can go a whole week without access to any water.

description:
Pokemon GO Vibrava is a ground dragon type with 1065 MAX CP.
Vibrava best moveset is Dragon Breath and Bulldoze.
Vibrava is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy type moves.
Vibrava is boosted by Clear and Wind weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Vibrava
pokedexEntry: Vibrava's wings have not yet completed the process of growing. Rather than flying long distances, they are more useful for generating ultrasonic waves by vibrating.

description:
Pokemon GO Flygon is a ground dragon type with 2458 MAX CP.
Flygon best moveset is Dragon Tail and Dragon Claw.
Flygon is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy type moves.
Flygon is boosted by Clear and Wind weather.
name: Flygon
pokedexEntry: Flygon whips up a sandstorm by flapping its wings. The wings create a series of notes that sound like singing. Because the “singing” is the only thing that can be heard in a sandstorm, this Pokemon is said to be the desert spirit.

description:
Pokemon GO Cacnea is a grass type with 1080 MAX CP.
Cacnea best moveset is Poison Sting and Grass Knot.
Cacnea is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice type moves.
Cacnea is boosted by Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Cacnea
pokedexEntry: The more arid and harsh the environment, the more pretty and fragrant a flower Cacnea grows. This Pokemon battles by wildly swinging its thorny arms.

description:
Pokemon GO Cacturne is a grass dark type with 2092 MAX CP.
Cacturne best moveset is Sucker Punch and Grass Knot.
Cacturne is vulnerable to Bug, Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice, Fairy, Fighting type moves.
Cacturne is boosted by
name: Cacturne
pokedexEntry: If a traveler is going through a desert in the thick of night, Cacturne will follow in a ragtag group. The Pokemon are biding their time, waiting for the traveler to tire and become incapable of moving.

description:
Pokemon GO Swablu is a normal flying type with 722 MAX CP.
Swablu best moveset is Peck and Aerial Ace.
Swablu is vulnerable to Rock, Ice, Electric type moves.
Swablu is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Wind weather.
It takes 400 candy to evolve!
name: Swablu
pokedexEntry: Swablu loves to make things clean. If it spots something dirty, it will wipe and polish it with its cottony wings. If its wings become dirty, this Pokemon finds a stream and showers itself.

description:
Pokemon GO Altaria is a dragon flying type with 1868 MAX CP.
Altaria best moveset is Dragon Breath and Sky Attack.
Altaria is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy, Rock type moves.
Altaria is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Altaria
pokedexEntry: Altaria sings in a gorgeous soprano. Its wings are like cotton clouds. This Pokemon catches updrafts with its buoyant wings and soars way up into the wild blue yonder.

description:
Pokemon GO Zangoose is a normal type with 2214 MAX CP.
Zangoose best moveset is Shadow Claw and Close Combat.
Zangoose is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Zangoose is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Zangoose
pokedexEntry: Zangoose usually stays on all fours, but when angered, it gets up on its hind legs and extends its claws. This Pokemon shares a bitter rivalry with Seviper that dates back over generations.

description:
Pokemon GO Seviper is a poison type with 1928 MAX CP.
Seviper best moveset is Poison Jab and Poison Fang.
Seviper is vulnerable to Ground, Psychic type moves.
Seviper is boosted by Cloudy weather.
name: Seviper
pokedexEntry: Seviper's swordlike tail serves two purposes—it slashes foes and douses them with secreted poison. This Pokemon will not give up its long-running blood feud with Zangoose.

description:
Pokemon GO Lunatone is a rock psychic type with 2245 MAX CP.
Lunatone best moveset is Confusion and Rock Slide.
Lunatone is vulnerable to Grass, Ground, Steel, Water, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Lunatone is boosted by
name: Lunatone
pokedexEntry: Lunatone becomes active around the time of the full moon. Instead of walking, it moves by floating in midair. The Pokemon's intimidating red eyes cause all those who see it to become transfixed with fear.

description:
Pokemon GO Solrock is a rock psychic type with 2245 MAX CP.
Solrock best moveset is Confusion and Solar Beam.
Solrock is vulnerable to Grass, Ground, Steel, Water, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Solrock is boosted by
name: Solrock
pokedexEntry: Sunlight is the source of Solrock's power. It is said to possess the ability to read the emotions of others. This Pokemon gives off intense heat while rotating its body.

description:
Pokemon GO Barboach is a water ground type with 716 MAX CP.
Barboach best moveset is Water Gun and Mud Bomb.
Barboach is vulnerable to Grass type moves.
Barboach is boosted by Rain and Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Barboach
pokedexEntry: Barboach's body is covered with a slimy film. If a foe grabs it, this Pokemon just slips out of the enemy's grip. This Pokemon grows weak if the slimy coating dries up.

description:
Pokemon GO Whiscash is a water ground type with 1991 MAX CP.
Whiscash best moveset is Water Gun and Mud Bomb.
Whiscash is vulnerable to Grass type moves.
Whiscash is boosted by Rain and Clear weather.
name: Whiscash
pokedexEntry: If Whiscash goes on a wild rampage, it sets off a quake-like tremor with a radius of over three miles. This Pokemon has the ability to predict real earthquakes.

description:
Pokemon GO Corphish is a water type with 1107 MAX CP.
Corphish best moveset is Bubble and Bubble Beam.
Corphish is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Corphish is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Corphish
pokedexEntry: Corphish catches prey with its sharp claws. It has no likes or dislikes when it comes to food—it will eat anything. This Pokemon has no trouble living in filthy water.

description:
Pokemon GO Crawdaunt is a water dark type with 2317 MAX CP.
Crawdaunt best moveset is Waterfall and Night Slash.
Crawdaunt is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Bug, Fairy, Fighting type moves.
Crawdaunt is boosted by Rain and Fog weather.
name: Crawdaunt
pokedexEntry: Crawdaunt molts (sheds) its shell regularly. Immediately after molting, its shell is soft and tender. Until the shell hardens, this Pokemon hides in its streambed burrow to avoid attack from its foes.

description:
Pokemon GO Baltoy is a ground psychic type with 676 MAX CP.
Baltoy best moveset is Confusion and Dig.
Baltoy is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Baltoy is boosted by Clear and Wind
name: Baltoy
pokedexEntry: As soon as it spots others of its kind, Baltoy congregates with them and then begins crying noisily in unison. This Pokemon sleeps while cleverly balancing itself on its one foot.

description:
Pokemon GO Claydol is a ground psychic type with 1782 MAX CP.
Claydol best moveset is Confusion and Earthquake.
Claydol is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Claydol is boosted by Clear and Wind
name: Claydol
pokedexEntry: Claydol is an enigma that appeared from a clay statue made by an ancient civilization dating back 20,000 years. This Pokemon shoots beams from both its hands.

description:
Pokemon GO Lileep is a rock grass type with 1181 MAX CP.
Lileep best moveset is Infestation and Grass Knot.
Lileep is vulnerable to Fighting, Steel, Bug, Ice type moves.
Lileep is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Clear weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Lileep
pokedexEntry: Lileep is an ancient Pokemon that was regenerated from a fossil. It remains permanently anchored to a rock. From its immobile perch, this Pokemon intently scans for prey with its two eyes.

description:
Pokemon GO Cradily is a rock grass type with 2081 MAX CP.
Cradily best moveset is Infestation and Grass Knot.
Cradily is vulnerable to Fighting, Steel, Bug, Ice type moves.
Cradily is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Clear weather.
name: Cradily
pokedexEntry: Cradily's body serves as an anchor, preventing it from being washed away in rough seas. This Pokemon secretes a strong digestive fluid from its tentacles.

description:
Pokemon GO Anorith is a rock bug type with 1310 MAX CP.
Anorith best moveset is Struggle Bug and Ancient Power.
Anorith is vulnerable to Steel, Water, Rock type moves.
Anorith is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Anorith
pokedexEntry: Anorith is said to be a type of Pokemon predecessor, with eight wings at the sides of its body. This Pokemon swam in the primordial sea by undulating these eight wings.

description:
Pokemon GO Armaldo is a rock bug type with 2675 MAX CP.
Armaldo best moveset is Fury Cutter and Rock Blast.
Armaldo is vulnerable to Steel, Water, Rock type moves.
Armaldo is boosted by PartlyCloudy and Rain weather.
name: Armaldo
pokedexEntry: Armaldo is a Pokemon species that became extinct in prehistoric times. This Pokemon is said to have walked on its hind legs, which would have been more convenient for life on land.

description:
Pokemon GO Feebas is a water type with 220 MAX CP.
Feebas best moveset is Tackle and Mirror Coat.
Feebas is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Feebas is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Feebas
pokedexEntry: While Feebas's body is in tatters, it has a hardy and tenacious life force that enables it to live anywhere. However, this Pokemon is also slow and dimwitted, making it an easy catch.

description:
Pokemon GO Milotic is a water type with 2967 MAX CP.
Milotic best moveset is Waterfall and Surf.
Milotic is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Milotic is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Milotic
pokedexEntry: Milotic live at the bottom of large lakes. When this Pokemon's body glows a vivid pink, it releases a pulsing wave of energy that brings soothing calm to troubled hearts.

description:
Pokemon GO Castform is a normal type with 1486 MAX CP.
Castform best moveset is Tackle and Stomp.
Castform is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Castform is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Castform
pokedexEntry: Castform borrows the power of nature to transform itself into the guises of the sun, rain, and snow-clouds. This Pokemon's feelings change with the weather.

description:
Pokemon GO Kecleon is a normal type with 1924 MAX CP.
Kecleon best moveset is Lick and Foul Play.
Kecleon is vulnerable to Fighting type moves.
Kecleon is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Kecleon
pokedexEntry: Kecleon alters its body coloration to blend in with its surroundings, allowing it to sneak up on its prey unnoticed. Then it lashes out with its long, stretchy tongue to instantly ensnare the unsuspecting target.

description:
Pokemon GO Shuppet is a ghost type with 872 MAX CP.
Shuppet best moveset is Feint Attack and Ominous Wind.
Shuppet is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost type moves.
Shuppet is boosted by Fog weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Shuppet
pokedexEntry: Shuppet grows by feeding on dark emotions, such as vengefulness and envy, in the hearts of people. It roams through cities in search of grudges that taint people.

description:
Pokemon GO Banette is a ghost type with 2073 MAX CP.
Banette best moveset is Shadow Claw and Shadow Ball.
Banette is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost type moves.
Banette is boosted by Fog weather.
name: Banette
pokedexEntry: A cursed energy permeated the stuffing of a discarded and forgotten plush doll, giving it new life as Banette. The Pokemon's energy would escape if it were to ever open its mouth.

description:
Pokemon GO Duskull is a ghost type with 523 MAX CP.
Duskull best moveset is Hex and Ominous Wind.
Duskull is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost type moves.
Duskull is boosted by Fog weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Duskull
pokedexEntry: Duskull wanders lost among the deep darkness of midnight. There is an oft-told admonishment given to misbehaving children that this Pokemon will spirit away bad children who earn scoldings from their mothers.

description:
Pokemon GO Dusclops is a ghost type with 1335 MAX CP.
Dusclops best moveset is Hex and Shadow Punch.
Dusclops is vulnerable to Dark, Ghost type moves.
Dusclops is boosted by Fog weather.
name: Dusclops
pokedexEntry: Dusclops absorbs anything, however large the object may be. This Pokemon hypnotizes its foe by waving its hands in a macabre manner and by bringing its single eye to bear. The hypnotized foe is made to do Dusclops's bidding.

description:
Pokemon GO Tropius is a grass flying type with 1846 MAX CP.
Tropius best moveset is Razor Leaf and Leaf Blade.
Tropius is vulnerable to Fire, Flying, Poison, Ice, Rock type moves.
Tropius is boosted by Clear and Wind weather.
name: Tropius
pokedexEntry: Children of the southern tropics eat as snacks the fruit that grows in bunches around the neck of Tropius. This Pokemon flies by flapping the leaves on its back as if they were wings.

description:
Pokemon GO Chimecho is a psychic type with 2095 MAX CP.
Chimecho best moveset is Extrasensory and Psyshock.
Chimecho is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Chimecho is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Chimecho
pokedexEntry: In high winds, Chimecho cries as it hangs from a tree branch or the eaves of a building using a suction cup on its head. This Pokemon plucks berries with its long tail and eats them.

description:
Pokemon GO Absol is a dark type with 2280 MAX CP.
Absol best moveset is Snarl and Dark Pulse.
Absol is vulnerable to Bug, Fairy, Fighting type moves.
Absol is boosted by Fog weather.
name: Absol
pokedexEntry: Absol has the ability to foretell the coming of natural disasters. It lives in a harsh, rugged mountain environment. This Pokemon very rarely ventures down from the mountains.

description:
Pokemon GO Wynaut is a psychic type with 503 MAX CP.
Wynaut best moveset is Counter and Mirror Coat.
Wynaut is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Wynaut is boosted by Wind weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Wynaut
pokedexEntry: Wynaut gather on moonlit nights to play by squeezing up against each other. By being squeezed, this Pokemon gains endurance and is trained to dole out powerful counterattacks.

description:
Pokemon GO Snorunt is a ice type with 772 MAX CP.
Snorunt best moveset is Powder Snow and Avalanche.
Snorunt is vulnerable to Fighting, Rock, Steel, Fire type moves.
Snorunt is boosted by Snow weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Snorunt
