pokedexEntry: Snorunt survives by eating only snow and ice. Old folklore claims that a house visited by this Pokemon is sure to prosper for many generations to come.

description:
Pokemon GO Glalie is a ice type with 1945 MAX CP.
Glalie best moveset is Ice Shard and Avalanche.
Glalie is vulnerable to Fighting, Rock, Steel, Fire type moves.
Glalie is boosted by Snow weather.
name: Glalie
pokedexEntry: Glalie has the ability to freely control ice. For example, it can instantly freeze its prey solid. After immobilizing its prey in ice, this Pokemon enjoys eating it in leisurely fashion.

description:
Pokemon GO Spheal is a ice water type with 876 MAX CP.
Spheal best moveset is Water Gun and Aurora Beam.
Spheal is vulnerable to Fighting, Rock, Electric, Grass type moves.
Spheal is boosted by Snow and Rain weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Spheal
pokedexEntry: Spheal always travels by rolling around on its ball-like body. When the season for ice floes arrives, this Pokemon can be seen rolling about on ice and crossing the sea.

description:
Pokemon GO Sealeo is a ice water type with 1607 MAX CP.
Sealeo best moveset is Water Gun and Aurora Beam.
Sealeo is vulnerable to Fighting, Rock, Electric, Grass type moves.
Sealeo is boosted by Snow and Rain weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Sealeo
pokedexEntry: Sealeo often balances and rolls things on the tip of its nose. While the Pokemon is rolling something, it checks the object's aroma and texture to determine whether it likes the object or not.

description:
Pokemon GO Walrein is a ice water type with 2606 MAX CP.
Walrein best moveset is Waterfall and Blizzard.
Walrein is vulnerable to Fighting, Rock, Electric, Grass type moves.
Walrein is boosted by Snow and Rain weather.
name: Walrein
pokedexEntry: Walrein swims all over in frigid seawater while crushing icebergs with its grand, imposing tusks. Its thick layer of blubber makes enemy attacks bounce off harmlessly.

description:
Pokemon GO Clamperl is a water type with 1091 MAX CP.
Clamperl best moveset is Water Gun and Water Pulse.
Clamperl is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Clamperl is boosted by Rain weather.
It takes 50 candy to evolve!
name: Clamperl
pokedexEntry: Clamperl grows while being protected by its rock-hard shell. When its body becomes too large to fit inside the shell, it is sure evidence that this Pokemon is getting close to evolution.

description:
Pokemon GO Huntail is a water type with 2140 MAX CP.
Huntail best moveset is Water Gun and Aqua Tail.
Huntail is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Huntail is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Huntail
pokedexEntry: Huntail's tail is shaped like a fish. It uses the tail to attract prey, then swallows the prey whole with its large, gaping mouth. This Pokemon swims by wiggling its slender body like a snake.

description:
Pokemon GO Gorebyss is a water type with 2281 MAX CP.
Gorebyss best moveset is Water Gun and Water Pulse.
Gorebyss is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Gorebyss is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Gorebyss
pokedexEntry: Although Gorebyss is the very picture of elegance and beauty while swimming, it is also cruel. When it spots prey, this Pokemon inserts its thin mouth into the prey's body and drains the prey of its body fluids.

description:
Pokemon GO Relicanth is a water rock type with 2557 MAX CP.
Relicanth best moveset is Water Gun and Hydro Pump.
Relicanth is vulnerable to Electric, Grass, Fighting, Ground type moves.
Relicanth is boosted by Rain and PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Relicanth
pokedexEntry: Relicanth is a rare species that was discovered in deep-sea explorations. This Pokemon's body withstands the enormous water pressure of the ocean depths. Its body is covered in tough scales that are like craggy rocks.

description:
Pokemon GO Luvdisc is a water type with 735 MAX CP.
Luvdisc best moveset is Water Gun and Water Pulse.
Luvdisc is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Luvdisc is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Luvdisc
pokedexEntry: Luvdisc's heart-shaped body is a symbol of love and romance. It is said that any couple meeting this Pokemon is promised a loving relationship that never ends.

description:
Pokemon GO Bagon is a dragon type with 1053 MAX CP.
Bagon best moveset is Bite and Flamethrower.
Bagon is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy type moves.
Bagon is boosted by Wind weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Bagon
pokedexEntry: Bagon harbors a never-ending dream of one day soaring high among the clouds. As if trying to dispel its frustration over its inability to fly, this Pokemon slams its hard head against huge rocks and shatters them into pebbles.

description:
Pokemon GO Shelgon is a dragon type with 1958 MAX CP.
Shelgon best moveset is Dragon Breath and Dragon Pulse.
Shelgon is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy type moves.
Shelgon is boosted by Wind weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Shelgon
pokedexEntry: Covering Shelgon's body are outgrowths much like bones. The shell is very hard and bounces off enemy attacks. When awaiting evolution, this Pokemon hides away in a cavern.

description:
Pokemon GO Salamence is a dragon flying type with 3532 MAX CP.
Salamence best moveset is Dragon Tail and Draco Meteor.
Salamence is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy, Rock type moves.
Salamence is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Salamence
pokedexEntry: By evolving into Salamence, this Pokemon finally realizes its long-held dream of growing wings. To express its joy, it flies and wheels all over the sky while spouting flames from its mouth.

description:
Pokemon GO Beldum is a steel psychic type with 843 MAX CP.
Beldum best moveset is Take Down and Struggle.
Beldum is vulnerable to Ground, Fire, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Beldum is boosted by Snow and Wind weather.
It takes 25 candy to evolve!
name: Beldum
pokedexEntry: Beldum keeps itself floating by generating a magnetic force that repels earth's natural magnetism. When it sleeps, this Pokemon anchors itself to a cliff using the hooks on its rear.

description:
Pokemon GO Metang is a steel psychic type with 1570 MAX CP.
Metang best moveset is Metal Claw and Psyshock.
Metang is vulnerable to Ground, Fire, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Metang is boosted by Snow and Wind weather.
It takes 100 candy to evolve!
name: Metang
pokedexEntry: When two Beldum fuse together, Metang is formed. The brains of the Beldum are joined by a magnetic nervous system. This Pokemon turns its arms to the rear for traveling at high speed.

description:
Pokemon GO Metagross is a steel psychic type with 3637 MAX CP.
Metagross best moveset is Bullet Punch and Psychic.
Metagross is vulnerable to Ground, Fire, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Metagross is boosted by Snow and Wind weather.
name: Metagross
pokedexEntry: Metagross is the result of two Metang achieving fusion. When hunting, this Pokemon pins the prey to the ground under its massive body. It then eats the helpless victim using the large mouth on its stomach.

description:
Pokemon GO Regirock is a rock type with 3087 MAX CP.
Regirock best moveset is Rock Throw and Stone Edge.
Regirock is vulnerable to Grass, Fighting, Ground, Steel, Water type moves.
Regirock is boosted by PartlyCloudy weather.
name: Regirock
pokedexEntry: Regirock's body is composed entirely of rocks. Recently, a study made the startling discovery that the rocks were all unearthed from different locations.

description:
Pokemon GO Regice is a ice type with 3087 MAX CP.
Regice best moveset is Frost Breath and Blizzard.
Regice is vulnerable to Fighting, Rock, Steel, Fire type moves.
Regice is boosted by Snow weather.
name: Regice
pokedexEntry: Regice cloaks itself with frigid air of -328 degrees Fahrenheit. Things will freeze solid just by going near this Pokemon. Its icy body is so cold, it will not melt even if it is immersed in magma.

description:
Pokemon GO Registeel is a steel type with 2261 MAX CP.
Registeel best moveset is Metal Claw and Flash Cannon.
Registeel is vulnerable to Fighting, Ground, Fire type moves.
Registeel is boosted by Snow weather.
name: Registeel
pokedexEntry: Registeel was imprisoned by people in ancient times. The metal composing its body is thought to be a curious substance that is not of this earth.

description:
Pokemon GO Latias is a dragon psychic type with 3377 MAX CP.
Latias best moveset is Dragon Breath and Dragon Claw.
Latias is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Latias is boosted by Wind
name: Latias
pokedexEntry: Latias is highly intelligent and capable of understanding human speech. It is covered with a glass-like down. The Pokemon enfolds its body with its down and refracts light to alter its appearance.

description:
Pokemon GO Latios is a dragon psychic type with 3644 MAX CP.
Latios best moveset is Dragon Breath and Dragon Claw.
Latios is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy, Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Latios is boosted by Wind
name: Latios
pokedexEntry: Latios will only open its heart to a Trainer with a compassionate spirit. This Pokemon can fly faster than a jet plane by folding its forelegs to minimize air resistance.

description:
Pokemon GO Kyogre is a water type with 4074 MAX CP.
Kyogre best moveset is Waterfall and Hydro Pump.
Kyogre is vulnerable to Electric, Grass type moves.
Kyogre is boosted by Rain weather.
name: Kyogre
pokedexEntry: Kyogre is said to be the personification of the sea itself. Legends tell of its many clashes against Groudon, as each sought to gain the power of nature.

description:
Pokemon GO Groudon is a ground type with 4074 MAX CP.
Groudon best moveset is Mud Shot and Earthquake.
Groudon is vulnerable to Grass, Ice, Water type moves.
Groudon is boosted by Clear weather.
name: Groudon
pokedexEntry: Through Primal Reversion and with nature's full power, it will take back its true form. It can cause magma to erupt and expand the landmass of the world.

description:
Pokemon GO Rayquaza is a dragon flying type with 3645 MAX CP.
Rayquaza best moveset is Dragon Tail and Outrage.
Rayquaza is vulnerable to Ice, Dragon, Fairy, Rock type moves.
Rayquaza is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Rayquaza
pokedexEntry: It flies forever through the ozone layer, consuming meteoroids for sustenance. The many meteoroids in its body provide the energy it needs to Mega Evolve.

description:
Pokemon GO Jirachi is a steel psychic type with 3090 MAX CP.
Jirachi best moveset is Confusion and Doom Desire.
Jirachi is vulnerable to Ground, Fire, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Jirachi is boosted by Snow and Wind weather.
name: Jirachi
pokedexEntry: Jirachi will awaken from its sleep of a thousand years if you sing to it in a voice of purity. It is said to make true any wish that people desire.

description:
Pokemon GO Deoxys is a psychic type with 15 MAX CP.
Deoxys best moveset is Counter and Zap Cannon.
Deoxys is vulnerable to Bug, Dark, Ghost type moves.
Deoxys is boosted by Wind weather.
name: Deoxys
pokedexEntry: Deoxys emerged from a virus that came from space. It is highly intelligent and wields psychokinetic powers. This Pokemon shoots lasers from the crystalline organ on its chest.
